ntent/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/171.jpg\" alt=\"17\" width=\"400\" height=\"600\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-105\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/181.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/181.jpg\" alt=\"18\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-106\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/191.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/191.jpg\" alt=\"19\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-107\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/201.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/201.jpg\" alt=\"20\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-108\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/212.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/212.jpg\" alt=\"21\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-109\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/221.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/221.jpg\" alt=\"22\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-110\" /></a>','【知非行记】大别山龙井河二号线重装穿越','','inherit','open','open','','90-revision-v1','','','2015-02-09 11:02:07','2015-02-09 03:02:07','',90,'http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/2015/02/09/90-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(114,1,'2015-02-09 11:06:39','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','自动草稿','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2015-02-09 11:06:39','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/?p=114',0,'post','',0),(115,1,'2015-02-09 13:46:39','2015-02-09 05:46:39','作者：chekiang\r\n\r\n早在上学的时候就听说过雨花石，后来机缘巧合来到南京才知道雨花石不是从雨花台那边捡的，雨花石的原产地主要是在六合那边。前些年和AA小伙伴一起去六合平山森林公园活动的途中，也曾经在路过的一个废弃的沙矿中捡过石头，时间短也没太多关注，所以也没捡到什么石头，但心中倒是落下了一个念想。当摄影群里的小伙伴提起捡雨花石的想法，马上就付诸于行动，组织一次六合捡石头及行摄南京的坝上草原活动……\r\n\r\n2014年7月13日，天气预报中的阵雨不见踪影，AA户外的十几辆车组成的捡石头车队浩浩荡荡滴开到了六合马鞍镇附近的一个沙矿，从此拉开一天的“疯狂石头之旅”……\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/113.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/113.jpg\" alt=\"1\" width=\"800\" height=\"531\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-120\" /></a>\r\n疯狂石头之旅部分成员的合影\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/213.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/213.jpg\" alt=\"2\" width=\"800\" height=\"531\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-121\" /></a>\r\nAA团队的车队，停靠在村边小路上\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/312.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/312.jpg\" alt=\"3\" width=\"800\" height=\"531\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-122\" /></a>\r\n提着各种工具和遮阳装备，前往沙矿\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/43.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/43.jpg\" alt=\"4\" width=\"800\" height=\"531\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-123\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/53.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/53.jpg\" alt=\"5\" width=\"800\" height=\"531\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-124\" /></a>\r\n满眼青翠，有没有草原的风范\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/63.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/63.jpg\" alt=\"6\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-125\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/73.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/73.jpg\" alt=\"7\" width=\"800\" height=\"531\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-126\" /></a>\r\n路边的小花\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/83.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/83.jpg\" alt=\"8\" width=\"800\" height=\"531\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-127\" /></a>\r\n抵达废弃的沙矿，这边已经长满了花草~~~\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/93.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/93.jpg\" alt=\"9\" width=\"800\" height=\"531\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-128\" /></a>\r\n大部分分散开，各自寻找自己心目中的石头~~\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/102.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/102.jpg\" alt=\"10\" width=\"800\" height=\"531\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-129\" /></a>\r\n天气热啊，我休息~~~\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/114.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/114.jpg\" alt=\"11\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-130\" /></a>\r\n天然木椅，我也来休息~~\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/122.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/122.jpg\" alt=\"12\" width=\"800\" height=\"531\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-131\" /></a>\r\n这边的大部队，还在继续奋斗在茫茫石堆中，寻觅，寻觅，不停地寻觅中……\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/132.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/132.jpg\" alt=\"13\" width=\"800\" height=\"531\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-132\" /></a>\r\n临近中午，耐不住的天气闷热，还有那紫外线的厉害，大家伙提着自己的战利品开始回程~~~\r\n\r\n六合横梁镇来一个土菜聚餐，然后到附近的雨花石交易市场观看和欣赏一下商家兜售的雨花石“精品”。原计划下午是准备去南京的坝上草原 -- 六合练山去行摄的，但大家对于雨花石的热情在经历了一上午的炙热天气考验之后丝毫未减，听取大家的意见下午继续在附近的正在开采矿区寻觅雨花石……\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/142.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/142.jpg\" alt=\"14\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-133\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/152.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/152.jpg\" alt=\"15\" width=\"800\" height=\"531\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-134\" /></a>\r\n\r\n临时决定的线路，临时询问的矿区地址，辛苦各位司机师傅们了，几经波折在周边绕了几圈终于来到心目中的正在开采的矿区。\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/162.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/162.jpg\" alt=\"16\" width=\"800\" height=\"531\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-116\" /></a>\r\n\r\n一直到六七点钟大家才恋恋不舍的告别沙矿，开始返回南京市区的返程。有人欢喜但没有人愁，无论是否捡到真正的雨花石，还是就捡了一堆鹅卵石……我们希望能捡到雨花石的上品、精品甚至珍品，但我们更享受的是捡石头过程的乐趣！\r\n最后秀一下我捡的一堆石头，鹅卵石也好看啊：\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/172.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/172.jpg\" alt=\"17\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-117\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/182.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/182.jpg\" alt=\"18\" width=\"800\" height=\"531\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-118\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/192.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/192.jpg\" alt=\"19\" width=\"800\" height=\"531\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-119\" /></a>\r\n\r\n【关于雨花石】\r\n\r\n雨花石是一种天然玛瑙石，也称文石，观赏石，幸运石，主要产于南京市六合区及仪征市月塘一带，是南京著名的特产。\r\n\r\n中国自南北朝以来，文人雅士寄情山水，啸傲烟霞，至唐宋时期达到巅峰，雅史趣事中有关赏石的佳话不胜枚举，神奇的雨花石更是成为石中珍品，有“石中皇后”之称，被誉为天赐国宝，中华一绝。\r\n\r\n雨花石的欣赏，追求的是“意境”，所谓景外之景，图外之画，弦外之音，无论诗情、画意、神采、文韵都包涵在意境之中，这就要求收藏者要有比较高的文化品位。一般提到雨花石人们通常会联想到南京雨花台，都以为雨花石就是产自雨花台一带，实际上这只是人们的误解。雨花石是世界观赏石中的一朵奇葩，有美丽的色彩和花纹，可供观赏。她主要产自扬子江畔、风光旖旎的南京六合。雨花石以“花”为名，花而冠雨、美丽迷人。\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n谢谢欣赏！~~~~\r\n','疯狂石头之旅 -- 记AA户外六合捡石头活动','','publish','open','open','','%e7%96%af%e7%8b%82%e7%9f%b3%e5%a4%b4%e4%b9%8b%e6%97%85-%e8%ae%b0aa%e6%88%b7%e5%a4%96%e5%85%ad%e5%90%88%e6%8d%a1%e7%9f%b3%e5%a4%b4%e6%b4%bb%e5%8a%a8','','','2015-02-09 13:46:39','2015-02-09 05:46:39','',0,'http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/?p=115',0,'post','',0),(116,1,'2015-02-09 13:35:29','2015-02-09 05:35:29','','16','','inherit','open','open','','16-3','','','2015-02-09 13:35:29','2015-02-09 05:35:29','',115,'http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/162.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(117,1,'2015-02-09 13:35:37','2015-02-09 05:35:37','','17','','inherit','open','open','','17-3','','','2015-02-09 13:35:37','2015-02-09 05:35:37','',115,'http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/172.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(118,1,'2015-02-09 13:35:44','2015-02-09 05:35:44','','18','','inherit','open','open','','18-3','','','2015-02-09 13:35:44','2015-02-09 05:35:44','',115,'http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/182.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(119,1,'2015-02-09 13:35:50','2015-02-09 05:35:50','','19','','inherit','open','open','','19-3','','','2015-02-09 13:35:50','2015-02-09 05:35:50','',115,'http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/192.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(120,1,'2015-02-09 13:35:57','2015-02-09 05:35:57','','1','','inherit','open','open','','1-4','','','2015-02-09 13:38:33','2015-02-09 05:38:33','',115,'http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/113.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(121,1,'2015-02-09 13:36:04','2015-02-09 05:36: