,'2015-02-09 10:04:52','',143,'http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/75.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(218,1,'2015-02-09 18:04:53','2015-02-09 10:04:53','','76','','inherit','open','open','','76','','','2015-02-09 18:04:53','2015-02-09 10:04:53','',143,'http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/76.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(219,1,'2015-02-09 18:04:54','2015-02-09 10:04:54','','77','','inherit','open','open','','77','','','2015-02-09 18:04:54','2015-02-09 10:04:54','',143,'http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/77.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(220,1,'2015-02-09 18:04:55','2015-02-09 10:04:55','','78','','inherit','open','open','','78','','','2015-02-09 18:04:55','2015-02-09 10:04:55','',143,'http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/78.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(221,1,'2015-02-09 18:04:55','2015-02-09 10:04:55','','79','','inherit','open','open','','79','','','2015-02-09 18:50:49','2015-02-09 10:50:49','',143,'http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/79.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(222,1,'2015-02-09 18:04:56','2015-02-09 10:04:56','','80','','inherit','open','open','','80','','','2015-02-09 18:04:56','2015-02-09 10:04:56','',143,'http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/80.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(223,1,'2015-02-09 18:04:57','2015-02-09 10:04:57','','81','','inherit','open','open','','81','','','2015-02-09 18:04:57','2015-02-09 10:04:57','',143,'http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/811.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(224,1,'2015-02-09 18:04:58','2015-02-09 10:04:58','','82','','inherit','open','open','','82','','','2015-02-09 18:04:58','2015-02-09 10:04:58','',143,'http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/821.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(225,1,'2015-02-09 18:52:41','2015-02-09 10:52:41','作者： 夜色扁扁\r\n前言：\r\n   尽管江南的春风，柔和的吹拂；尽管金陵的旭日，温情的照耀；尽管烈日的灼伤，已经消退；尽管。。。 。。。\r\n   而鳌太，我的心还在行走，在白雪皑皑的丛林，在巨石狰狞的石海，在狂风暴吼的夜晚。。。 。。。\r\n   有许多山野在岁月里淡隐，鳌太永远则是昨天的脚步，一个个艰难前行的背影，时常在记忆里跋涉。\r\n\r\n   鳌太穿越已经结束10多日，前前后后也有诸多笔墨渲染，现今重新梳理，记录旅行中的那些美好，那些喜悦，和奔放的生命里的一丝感伤。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/W11_7533-e1423475551927.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/W11_7533-e1423475551927.jpg\" alt=\"W11_7533\" width=\"750\" height=\"454\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-141\" /></a>\r\n新春鳌太，奔放的生命\r\n\r\n   队员：\r\n   好人锅，战狼版版主，沉着稳重，有着狼塔，乌孙，夏特，千八，独竖尖等多条著名户外顶级线路的丰富经验，本次活动召集人，筹备人，前后功课笔记若干，苦口良言若干。活动中，背负20余天口粮，在最艰难的时刻，使得队伍从容淡定。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/214-e1423476376670.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/214-e1423476376670.jpg\" alt=\"2\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-144\" /></a>\r\n阿生，广东强人，据说多年前就和华女军胶牛仔徒步墨脱，对国内顶级虐线趋之若鹜。本次活动，背负冰镐，绳索等公共装备，体能惊人，处惊不变，二次滑坠中化险为夷。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/313-e1423476445410.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/313-e1423476445410.jpg\" alt=\"3\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-145\" /></a>\r\n华女，女神级强驴，12年狼塔CV连穿，让一帮男人望尘莫及，鳌太穿越依然健步如飞。专业级随队医生，伤病克星，同行很踏实。<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/44-e1423476499428.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/44-e1423476499428.jpg\" alt=\"4\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-146\" /></a>\r\n\r\n雪梨，体能充沛，持久性金霸王，狼塔，鳌太等虐线淡定自若，行云流水般在高山雪原轻盈而过。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/54-e1423476555958.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/54-e1423476555958.jpg\" alt=\"5\" width=\"750\" height=\"493\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-147\" /></a>\r\n夜色，楼主，走过鳌太，千八，小五等知名强线，乱爬过四姑娘山，毕棚沟不知名雪山，喜欢野行胡走。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/64-e1423476597486.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/64-e1423476597486.jpg\" alt=\"6\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-148\" /></a>\r\n2月11日\r\n   7点半，众人包车从西安出发，因冰雪路滑，下午2点方到达塘口。分好气罐公共装备后，开始进山。路面有雪，和国庆来时已面目全非，若不是好人锅叫唤，估计就从田里切过去了，看到山就兴奋，刹不住双腿。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/74-e1423476632297.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/74-e1423476632297.jpg\" alt=\"7\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-149\" /></a>\r\n 山脚下好人锅放鞭洒酒，以敬山神。\r\n   虽然不到2000的海拔，但是积雪已经深厚，爬起来比较吃力。2个小时左右，上升到海拔1979处，有一平坡，风平水净，大伙开心扎营。只有楼主刚走的兴起，继续前行的欲望比较强烈。\r\n   5点搭好帐篷，点火烧饭。晚，百无聊赖中，幸得信号，欣喜的QQ小扯。<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/84-e1423476710117.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/84-e1423476710117.jpg\" alt=\"8\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-150\" /></a>\r\n2月12日\r\n   起营时听到有人叫唤，疑为森林管理员，瞬间紧张了一把。12年鳌太山难震惊世人，有关部门加强戒备，冬季严禁穿越。待人近眼前，方知是一早从塘口出发穿越鳌山的河南山友。细询之下，竟然遇到狼塔群的朋友，狗子和韩湘子，非常开心。\r\n道别后，河南队伍先行，我们迟迟缓缓近10点动身，一时不适应好人锅的慢生活，尤其心焦。<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/94-e1423476739348.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/94-e1423476739348.jpg\" alt=\"9\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-151\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/103-e1423476763632.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/103-e1423476763632.jpg\" alt=\"10\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-152\" /></a>\r\n下午两点到达垭口，宽阔的跑马梁收入眼底，心驰神往。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/115-e1423476814949.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/115-e1423476814949.jpg\" alt=\"11\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-153\" /></a>\r\n过药棚子后，跟着河南队伍的脚印走错一段，以致天黑才感到2900营地。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/123-e1423476849924.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/123-e1423476849924.jpg\" alt=\"12\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-154\" /></a>\r\n河南队伍受此延误，同宿一营。\r\n   海拔升高，天寒地冻，没有丝毫流水，从此过上吃雪的日子。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/133-e1423477007679.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/133-e1423477007679.jpg\" alt=\"13\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-155\" /></a>\r\n2月13日\r\n   在此起彼伏的呼噜里醒来，烦躁的等待中，好人锅准时叫早。6点半，天色未明，正如下午7点天色未暗的西部特色。\r\n   经管8点多就打好包，从容沉着的好人锅依然坚守3小时拔营的作风，放任楼主的背包无助的期待，10点左右不急不忙的出发。<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/143-e1423477040584.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/143-e1423477040584.jpg\" alt=\"14\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-156\" /></a>\r\n天气没预期的好，或许夜里就已经转阴，清早时时飞起碎雪，走入丛林后风雪渐强。在盆景园，狂风一度达到9级左右，温度也下降到零下15。在恶劣的气候环境下，河南队伍不久下撤，除了狗子和悠然投奔过来。不久气温稍有上升，好人锅放弃扎营的念头，队伍向导航架靠近。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/153-e1423477101179.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/153-e1423477101179.jpg\" alt=\"15\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-157\" /></a>\r\n下午三点，没及时察觉GPS低温抽疯，在石海里上下左右折腾个8字麻花。因为开路，楼主非常狼狈，把大伙整的心碎直接要求扎营。\r\n   4点多，切回轨迹，大家就地扎营，抚慰心痛。\r\n   6点半，好人锅欢呼天气转好，楼主兴奋出账。果然阴云消散，导航架露出真身。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/164-e1423477137438.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/164-e1423477137438.jpg\" alt=\"16\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-158\" /></a>\r\n2月14日\r\n   情人节，没有阳光，没有问候，一路风雪迈向导航架。天气不算太糟糕，不常见到暴风雪，倒让人有点激动，只是石海比往常爬的艰难，得双杖捣雪探路，要是栽进石坑伤了，活着也大多是等待牺牲的到来。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/173-e1423477177639.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/173-e1423477177639.jpg\" alt=\"17\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-159\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/183-e1423477205830.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/183-e1423477205830.jpg\" alt=\"18\" width=\"750\" height=\"478\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-160\" /></a><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/193-e1423477225732.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/193-e1423477225732.jpg\" alt=\"19\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-161\" /></a>\r\n下午2点，顺利抵达导航架，附近有新鲜脚印，看来有人慕名来拜。\r\n   鳌山重要标志，尽情作秀，疯狂弄姿。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/202-e1423477257175.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/202-e1423477257175.jpg\" alt=\"20\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-162\" /></a><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/215-e1423477279733.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/215-e1423477279733.jpg\" alt=\"21\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-163\" /></a>\r\n河南伙伴如愿登临导航架后，惺惺而别，我们则挥师药王庙。\r\n   西跑马梁暴风长吼，积雪难留，冰壳满路，预料中白毛风让人战栗。无处避风，要不好人锅很有可能下令扎营，楼主暗喜能多虐几步。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/222-e1423477314727.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/222-e1423477314727.jpg\" alt=\"22\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-164\" /></a>\r\n6点终于可以近身拜药王，一路牵挂的鞭炮和二锅头扛了今天终于永别，漫漫旅程不再羁绊，磨破的双跨伤愈可待，身心舒畅。\r\n   晚，天气貌似又有好转，内心又开始小激动，思绪连绵。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/231-e1423477347488.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/231-e1423477347488.jpg\" alt=\"23\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-165\" /></a>\r\n2月15日\r\n   出帐篷看到天气大好，风景大好，自然心情大好。日出，期待了几天后，如愿而至。各种照片，各种秀，各种美，粉墨登场。原以为冰镐不会派上用场，今天有幸成为摄影道具，走上把文艺线。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/241-e1423477385161.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/241-e1423477385161.jpg\" alt=\"24\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-166\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/251-e1423477446849.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/251-e1423477446849.jpg\" alt=\"25\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-167\" /></a><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/261-e1423477467612.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/261-e1423477467612.jpg\" alt=\"26\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-168\" /></a><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/271-e1423477485995.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/271-e1423477485995.jpg\" alt=\"27\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-169\" /></a>\r\n每每幸逢日出，楼主总是满心喜悦，有一种再生的感觉在血脉涌动，兴奋之下，在药王庙前后上串下跳。\r\n   10点左右，开始翻越麦桔岭。山脊之上，白毛风，西北风，飓风，旋风，若干风狂奔。暴风中，双腿想停下来还得费一番心思。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/281-e1423477522816.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/281-e1423477522816.jpg\" alt=\"28\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-170\" /></a>\r\n风吼云翻，晴阴轮回只是眨眼之际，一时间为天地造化折服。茫茫石海，渺小的身姿在暴风里爬动，生命是脆弱，还是坚强，一时困惑！<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/291-e1423477554920.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/291-e1423477554920.jpg\" alt=\"29\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-171\" /></a><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/301-e1423477578425.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/301-e1423477578425.jpg\" alt=\"30\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-172\" /></a>\r\n下午3点，翻上最后一座岭后，下错山梁。虽然50米的海拔，但是遭受麦桔岭的崩溃消耗，一个小坡就让脆弱的心不堪伤痛，于是有伙伴提出扎营。而天色尚早，营地狭小，危居陡坡实在忐忑，大家商议后决定下坡，垭口扎营。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/314-e1423477611766.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/314-e1423477611766.jpg\" alt=\"31\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-173\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/321-e1423477634812.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/321-e1423477634812.jpg\" alt=\"32\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-174\" /></a>\r\n5点，从乱石横生的积雪草坡，缓步下降到垭口，在深雪里踩雪扎营。\r\n   晚餐继续帐篷里有条不紊的落实。\r\n   夜里暴风，楼主依靠巨石得以安睡。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/331-e1423477679114.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/331-e1423477679114.jpg\" alt=\"33\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-175\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/341-e1423477699532.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/341-e1423477699532.jpg\" alt=\"34\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-176\" /></a>\r\n2月16日\r\n     天气晴好，心情大悦，在耀眼的阳光中翻越乱石雪坡，辛苦而快乐。上山梁，对面的麦桔岭和盘托出，丝毫不觉昨日狂风大雾里的凶险。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/351-e1423477730279.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/351-e1423477730279.jpg\" alt=\"35\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-177\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/361-e1423477756813.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/361-e1423477756813.jpg\" alt=\"36\" width=\"750\" height=\"402\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-178\" /></a>\r\n梁下一面云海滔滔，浩瀚无际，一面则云雾飘渺，如梦如幻。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/371-e1423477791709.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/371-e1423477791709.jpg\" alt=\"37\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-179\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/381-e1423477816578.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/381-e1423477816578.jpg\" alt=\"38\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-180\" /></a>\r\n下午下梁，向梁一行进。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/391-e1423477854435.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/391-e1423477854435.jpg\" alt=\"39\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-181\" /></a>\r\n过一小树林，风景绝美，云腾烟舞，时在云雾里穿行，实在阳光下翻坡，恍若天境。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/401-e1423477893742.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/401-e1423477893742.jpg\" alt=\"40\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-182\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/411-e1423477920656.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/411-e1423477920656.jpg\" alt=\"41\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-183\" /></a><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/421-e1423477942158.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/421-e1423477942158.jpg\" alt=\"42\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-184\" /></a>\r\n楼主童心大发，绕道登山远眺，不经意中，惊逢佛光，尘事未了，而佛缘早至。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/431-e1423477977388.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/431-e1423477977388.jpg\" alt=\"43\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-185\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/441-e1423478002668.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/441-e1423478002668.jpg\" alt=\"44\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-186\" /></a>\r\n梁一下一垭口，为避开积雪好人锅建议右切，途中阿生遭遇滑坠，果然经历狂风巨浪之士，处惊不乱，及时刹车。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/45-e1423478033102.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/45-e1423478033102.jpg\" alt=\"45\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-187\" /></a>\r\n 惊魂不久，大雾中不小心又切错山梁，天色暗及时止步扎营。稍时狂风大作，气温急降，楼主从坡上收集了一塑料袋残雪，便匆匆进账。该坡丛林不乏而积雪甚少，可见狂风乃家常便饭。\r\n   \r\n2月17日\r\n   清晨，好人锅高呼直接起营去垭口早餐，正合楼主心意，睡石坑食脏雪，分秒不想多呆。抖抖冰霜满结的帐篷，擦掉睡袋的冰渣，挤进笨重的冰鞋，上路！\r\n   回眸睡过的斜坡，野猪窝不如，一阵悲壮，据说有伙伴深夜被狂风吹得在帐篷里翻跟斗。\r\n   如好人锅所料，丹娜军靴不知何时开裂，负了主人一番深意，果然远非神器，不禁怅然。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/46-e1423478067109.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/46-e1423478067109.jpg\" alt=\"46\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-188\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/47-e1423478089983.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/47-e1423478089983.jpg\" alt=\"47\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-189\" /></a>\r\n餐后开始整天的雪雾大风中切梁翻海，梁一，梁二，梁三，梁梁索命，稍不小心扭伤腿都是致命的。梁一乱石坡尤其恐怖，巨石深坑，每一步都再三思量。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/48-e1423478120611.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/48-e1423478120611.jpg\" alt=\"48\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-190\" /></a>\r\n下午下梁三，过凤凰腰，在小树林里因深雪阻拦，天暗人疲，2800营地生饭安睡成为奢望。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/49-e1423478152114.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/49-e1423478152114.jpg\" alt=\"49\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/50-e1423478173981.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/50-e1423478173981.jpg\" alt=\"50\" width=\"750\" height=\"523\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-192\" /></a>\r\n晚在林子扎营，玉树琼枝，细雪轻落，虽然美景虚设，凭空臆想也自一番况味。\r\n\r\n2月18日\r\n   清晨出帐，见一夜新雪，兴奋，新奇，一时间心思飞扬，若干个想象在脑海风驰电擎。。。。。。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/511-e1423478213693.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/511-e1423478213693.jpg\" alt=\"51\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-193\" /></a>\r\n深雪里一腿深一腿浅的从小树林跋涉到2800营地，雪雾弥漫，狂风不歇，只得上山入林小憩。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/521-e1423478248399.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/521-e1423478248399.jpg\" alt=\"52\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-194\" /></a>\r\n林里上坡的雪愈发深不可测，几番陷坑的挣扎，让人身惫心怯。风雪交加里，望望茫茫的丛林，一阵心寒。想到东源还有大片恐怖的丛林，一时间茫然。休息片刻后，强打精神开路，数米后又栽深坑，两腿在石缝里艰难的交错发力。老雪挤住双腿，新雪难以得力，身负重包，不折腾个人仰马翻，休想爬处雪坑，用力过猛，左膝盖关节轻微扭伤。\r\n    喘息中，想到恶劣天气导致的10多天甚至20多天穿越，想到朋友在牵挂，想到亲人正忧心，想到即将上班，想到伤病，想到山难，想到生，想到死。。。。。\r\n    种种懊恼的景象，在暴风雪里旋转，直教人眩晕，心力难支。于是征询好人锅意见，是否需要下撤。\r\n    好人锅扛了20多天食物，淡然道，先走，看明天天气。其他伙伴也是一脸从容。阿生见楼主疲乏，上前接过开路的活，杖刨脚踩，左试右探，或跪或爬，继续艰难的脚步。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/531-e1423478281639.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/531-e1423478281639.jpg\" alt=\"53\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-195\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/541-e1423478304347.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/541-e1423478304347.jpg\" alt=\"54\" width=\"750\" height=\"490\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-196\" /></a>\r\n下午六点，扎营间，天色见好，西天着彩，满心喜悦和期待。晚点篝火未果，严寒中赶紧入帐安睡。\r\n\r\n2月19日\r\n   上苍终是怜悯，天气格外的晴朗。兴奋之极，大伙还在打包，楼主就蹭蹭的开路了。尽管依然有深坑，而风轻云淡，天开阔心亦豁达，辛苦而喜悦的穿丛林，翻乱石，登上大金字塔。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/55-e1423478332965.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/55-e1423478332965.jpg\" alt=\"55\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-197\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/56-e1423478354802.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/56-e1423478354802.jpg\" alt=\"56\" width=\"750\" height=\"1036\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-198\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/57-e1423478376588.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/57-e1423478376588.jpg\" alt=\"57\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-199\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/58-e1423478403789.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/58-e1423478403789.jpg\" alt=\"58\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-200\" /></a>\r\n上塔后，一路云烟一路蓝天，脚步轻盈，心情荡漾。艰辛历经之处，美色铺陈；气喘人溃之时，仙境忽临。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/59-e1423478431575.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/59-e1423478431575.jpg\" alt=\"59\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-201\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/60-e1423478453272.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/60-e1423478453272.jpg\" alt=\"60\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-202\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/611-e1423478482957.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/611-e1423478482957.jpg\" alt=\"61\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-203\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/621-e1423478504380.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/621-e1423478504380.jpg\" alt=\"62\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-204\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/631-e1423478531507.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/631-e1423478531507.jpg\" alt=\"63\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-205\" /></a>\r\n翻过塔一塔二，晚在塔三下垭口扎营。面向云海，看潮起潮落；背靠巨石，听风过风往。一夜心飞，随风吹云涌！\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/641-e1423478579377.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/641-e1423478579377.jpg\" alt=\"64\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-206\" /></a>\r\n2月20日\r\n   告别塔三，迈向九层石海，登天揽月，拂云吞雾，天与地的距离只在一念之间。  \r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/65-e1423478606500.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/65-e1423478606500.jpg\" alt=\"65\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-207\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/66-e1423478634558.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/66-e1423478634558.jpg\" alt=\"66\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-208\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/67-e1423478670778.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/67-e1423478670778.jpg\" alt=\"67\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-209\" /></a>\r\n登上九层石海，乃知真的王。前望，飞机诸梁，金字诸塔，峰峰入海；转身，太白大梁，秦岭主峰，云烟飘渺。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/68-e1423478711435.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/68-e1423478711435.jpg\" alt=\"68\" width=\"750\" height=\"448\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-210\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/69-e1423478731609.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/69-e1423478731609.jpg\" alt=\"69\" width=\"750\" height=\"468\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-211\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/70-e1423478760907.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/70-e1423478760907.jpg\" alt=\"70\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-212\" /></a>\r\n下午6点经太白梁，落日西沉，山野披彩，在大石河林地的山脊，楼主独守夕阳，为那即逝的美。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/711-e1423478795787.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/711-e1423478795787.jpg\" alt=\"71\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-213\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/721-e1423478815990.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/721-e1423478815990.jpg\" alt=\"72\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-214\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/731-e1423478854851.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/731-e1423478854851.jpg\" alt=\"73\" width=\"750\" height=\"467\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-215\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/741-e1423478897372.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/741-e1423478897372.jpg\" alt=\"74\" width=\"750\" height=\"497\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-216\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/75-e1423478916523.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/75-e1423478916523.jpg\" alt=\"75\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-217\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/76-e1423478960416.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/76-e1423478960416.jpg\" alt=\"76\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-218\" /></a>\r\n晚，扎营大石河林地，星光满天，雪林静默，天晴出山早，心坦，淡淡的思念里入睡。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/77-e1423478990549.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/77-e1423478990549.jpg\" alt=\"77\" width=\"750\" height=\"489\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-219\" /></a>\r\n2月21日\r\n   离开营地，风云再起，深雪里翻越东源。  \r\n   著名的迷魂阵，半点不得含糊，12年国庆曾在此误入歧途，此刻雪雾迷眼，更加扑朔迷离。经导航架，麦桔岭，梁一垭口的几段迷途之痛，每一个行程都前瞻后顾，左右思量，频频掏出挂在脖上塞在怀里的GPS比对路迹，好人锅也在后面一路用指北针核证方向。  \r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/78-e1423479021550.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/78-e1423479021550.jpg\" alt=\"78\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-220\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/79-e1423479045163.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/79-e1423479045163.jpg\" alt=\"79\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-221\" /></a>\r\n下午踏上跑马梁，沿箭头直奔大爷海。\r\n    二爷海垭口处有飘忽的信号，众人试拨电话，半成半败的在寒风里折腾一刻。此番折腾后，竟烟沉云散，美丽的夕阳磅礴而出。\r\n   有些挫折命中难躲，有些美好也注定了相逢，珍惜当前，细细感受。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/80-e1423479072986.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/80-e1423479072986.jpg\" alt=\"80\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/811-e1423479088334.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/811-e1423479088334.jpg\" alt=\"81\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223\" /></a>\r\n晚，入住大爷海客栈，不再钻冰霜冰洁的帐篷和睡袋，无风无雪的沉睡。\r\n   2月22日，一早轻装拔仙台，回客栈背包下山。\r\n   20公里的陡坡和栈道，一直走到天暗月明。\r\n   铁甲树下，众人协力，终于联系了净水鸟的张老板前来接人饱餐，连夜送往西安。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/821-e1423479115213.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/821-e1423479115213.jpg\" alt=\"82\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224\" /></a>\r\n2月23日\r\n   2点，入住西门格林豪泰。\r\n   风风雪雪鳌太穿越，远去!   \r\n  \r\n后记：\r\n    许多人谈论过旅行的意义，有人说是平淡生活的一种调剂，一份开心；有认说旅行在于一种新感触，新视野；还有人的旅行，是对现实的逃避，对世俗的抗争。\r\n   冬穿鳌太，或许已经超越旅行的界定，探险的意味甚浓。可能一些心智正常的人，认为那是群精神病。这年头，不乏被精神病，所以淡然一笑。\r\n   我之对于户外，不外乎风景，一种原始的，不受侵染的美色。而大凡这些风景，已经远离人类文明，于是不得不翻山涉水，于是就所谓自虐。如果身边有风景，谁会走天涯？\r\n   我之对于户外，不外乎风景，一种超越风景本身的风景。当所谓自虐，成为一种快乐，跋山涉水也自有愉悦。以原始的力量和智慧，贴近真实的世界，是人本性的追求。于是，身边有风景，也欲走天涯。\r\n   我之对于户外，依然为风景。每每，身边的人，身边的事，当不可企及，而情感只有于山野荒漠得以流泻，受冰雪之覆以退烧，握死神之手方坚强。远行，只想淡忘身边的风景，为他，为她，为一个美丽的无奈的梦。于是，身边有风景，才会走天涯！ \r\n   \r\n特别感谢：\r\n   部分珍贵照片借用好人锅和阿生。','奔放的青春——记冬鳌太极限穿越','','inherit','open','open','','143-revision-v1','','','2015-02-09 18:52:41','2015-02-09 10:52:41','',143,'http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/2015/02/09/143-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(226,1,'2015-02-09 19:01:36','2015-02-09 11:01:36','作者：疯者寒冰 \r\n\r\n没有华丽的文字，只想对大家说，虽然人回来了，但心留在了那里！\r\n\r\n继续前行，更多更美的地方在等着我们……\r\n\r\n谢谢一起走过的20位伙伴\r\n\r\n谢谢色大\r\n\r\n寒冰加油！<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/216.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/216.jpg\" alt=\"2\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-227\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/116.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/116.jpg\" alt=\"11\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\