empie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/117-e1423480436784.jpg\" alt=\"1\" width=\"750\" height=\"194\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-254\" /></a>\r\n经过十几个小时的车程才到达沈子村，在山下看着山上的云彩变幻，让人不禁期待山上的壮丽风景，而实际等待着我们的却是狂风大雨，从山脚往上没走多远天空就飘起了小雨，一路上淅淅沥沥满眼雨雾，我和小伙伴们走在队伍的最后成了临时的收队，等我们快到山顶的时候能见度已经很低了，走在山脊上顶着狂风大作向金顶蹒跚而去，因为天气的缘故我们只好放弃了露营的打算，小伙伴们一起住进了金顶了简陋客栈，算上第二天我们倒是白白背了三天的帐篷。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/218.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/218.jpg\" alt=\"2\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-255\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/315.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/315.jpg\" alt=\"3\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-256\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/410.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/410.jpg\" alt=\"4\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-257\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/510.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/510.jpg\" alt=\"5\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-258\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/610.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/610.jpg\" alt=\"6\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-259\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/710-e1423480484675.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/710-e1423480484675.jpg\" alt=\"7\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-260\" /></a>\r\n清晨还未睁眼就听到外面雨点打在客栈顶棚的声音，于是赖在睡袋里将起床的时间一拖再拖，直到雨声渐止外面人声四起，收拾好东西准备吃早饭的当口听到外面有人兴奋地大呼云海，立马饭也不吃抓起相机就往外跑，外面好多人已经等好一会了，雾气时起时散，群山在云雾里隐约可见，一天的行程就在如此精彩的风景后开始了\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/85.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/85.jpg\" alt=\"8\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-261\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/95.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/95.jpg\" alt=\"9\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-262\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/104.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/104.jpg\" alt=\"10\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-263\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/118-e1423480535413.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/118-e1423480535413.jpg\" alt=\"11\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-264\" /></a>\r\n队伍在金顶合影后差不多9点出发前往发云界，路上翻过一个又一个的山头，追着雾气消散的节奏，等待着太阳的出现，遗憾的是武功群山只是偶露峥嵘，放眼四顾只是茫茫一片，在满是期待和无奈中先行来到了发云界绿缘客栈（待续……）\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/125.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/125.jpg\" alt=\"12\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-265\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/135.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/135.jpg\" alt=\"13\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-266\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/145.j