loads/sites/2/2015/02/2110.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(309,1,'2015-02-09 19:21:49','2015-02-09 11:21:49','','22','','inherit','open','open','','22-6','','','2015-02-09 19:21:49','2015-02-09 11:21:49','',287,'http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/225.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(310,1,'2015-02-09 19:21:49','2015-02-09 11:21:49','','23','','inherit','open','open','','23-5','','','2015-02-09 19:21:49','2015-02-09 11:21:49','',287,'http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/234.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(311,1,'2015-02-09 19:26:33','2015-02-09 11:26:33','作者： 夜色扁扁\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/119-e1423480912550.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/119-e1423480912550.jpg\" alt=\"1\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-288\" /></a>\r\n一场千里迢迢的奔走，只为一朵花的绽放.\r\n一段牵肠挂肚的感情，只为一颗心的萌动.\r\n小五之恋，写在盛夏！\r\n\r\n   有些人，走过了，还是恋恋不忘；有些风景，走过了，也是再三思量。12年的小五，有许多的感动，虽然脚步匆匆再匆匆。岁月流转，又是一年夏风起，又是一年金莲开，小五，我们再次相拥!\r\n   7月4日，晚7点，仰慕小五芳名的39位伙伴，齐聚南京玄武门，集体包车远赴河北蔚县。\r\n   经过近一天一夜的长途跋涉，7月5日下去终于到达赤崖堡，中国十大非著名山峰之一，小五台的脚下。办理了冗余繁杂的进山手续后，4点40，开始进山。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/220.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/220.jpg\" alt=\"2\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-289\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/317-e1423480953655.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/317-e1423480953655.jpg\" alt=\"3\" width=\"750\" height=\"473\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-290\" /></a>\r\n美好的事物，往往都需要一番艰难的周折才能接近，小五也不例外。必须经过死人坡的痛苦历练，才能近嗅满山的芬芳。一路上，听到的尽是短促的喘息，看到的尽是大汗淋漓的脸。\r\n   晚9点左右，疲惫的双腿终于踏上北台山脊，此为北一垭口，草地略有开阔，比较平整，于是就此扎营。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/412-e1423480989554.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/412-e1423480989554.jpg\" alt=\"4\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-291\" /></a>\r\n夜晚，星光灿烂，月色朦胧，酒后吹吹凉风，看看美景，疲乏渐退。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/512.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/512.jpg\" alt=\"5\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-292\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/612-e1423481014591.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/612-e1423481014591.jpg\" alt=\"6\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-293\" /></a>\r\n因为牵挂前队的伙伴，天未明人已醒，4点40从营地出发，独身前往探视。连过北二北三几个垭口和营地，一直到北台才赶上正在早餐的前队，此刻5点半，太阳已老早的升起。\r\n   伙伴们经昨日的强烈攀升和清晨的匆匆赶路，此刻近半疲惫不堪，纷纷表示量力而行，走到哪是哪，不再纠结于拜谒几台。\r\n   昨日波澜壮阔的豪情壮志，今天开始归于平静。回想自己曾经意气风发的旅行，在风风雨雨之后，也往往如此。艰难困苦，会让狂野的心趋向淡泊和安宁。。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/712.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/712.jpg\" alt=\"7\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-294\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/86.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/86.jpg\" alt=\"8\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-295\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/96.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/96.jpg\" alt=\"9\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-296\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/105-e1423481054540.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/105-e1423481054540.jpg\" alt=\"10\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-297\" /></a>\r\n5点50，登上北台。怀念去年邂逅的佛光，而一再徘徊。机缘总是可遇不可求，在北台顶等待20分钟，无果返回。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/1110.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/1110.jpg\" alt=\"11\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-298\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/126.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/126.jpg\" alt=\"12\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-299\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/136.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/136.jpg\" alt=\"13\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-300\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/146.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/146.jpg\" alt=\"14\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-301\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/156.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/156.jpg\" alt=\"15\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-302\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/167.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/167.jpg\" alt=\"16\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-303\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/176.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/176.jpg\" alt=\"17\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-304\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/186.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/186.jpg\" alt=\"18\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-305\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/196-e1423481121871.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/196-e1423481121871.jpg\" alt=\"19\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-306\" /></a>\r\n6点50，赶回营地。\r\n   7点30，穿越二台的伙伴开始出发。\r\n   在都市禁锢的越久，我们的心，越向往山野，那纯净清凉的空气，那自由奔放的花朵，那座青山，那片蓝天，都是无法抵抗的诱惑。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/205.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/205.jpg\" alt=\"20\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-307\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/2110.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/2110.jpg\" alt=\"21\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-308\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/225.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/225.jpg\" alt=\"22\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-309\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/234-e1423481163342.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/234-e1423481163342.jpg\" alt=\"23\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-310\" /></a>','盛夏的小五之恋（一）','','inherit','open','open','','287-revision-v1','','','2015-02-09 19:26:33','2015-02-09 11:26:33','',287,'http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/2015/02/09/287-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(312,1,'2015-02-09 19:35:01','2015-02-09 11:35:01','作者：清泉慧\r\n走！\r\n背着行囊，带着自己，向远方出发，向未知出发！\r\n去体验过程，去征服未知！去享受快乐！\r\n这个过程充满未知，这个征服需要毅力，这个快乐不是谁都懂！\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/120-e1423481406572.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/120-e1423481406572.jpg\" alt=\"1\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-313\" /></a>\r\n有句经典台词：皇上，您还记得大明湖畔的夏雨荷吗？\r\n咱篡改一下：伙伴们，我们能找到大明山上的冬雪松吗？\r\n11月8-9号，细雨沥沥冷风瑟瑟，浙江临安大明山脚下，有这么一群人，雾气氤氲烟雨萦绕中昂首阔步，想要用双脚去丈量山的高度，想要用双眼去俯瞰大自然的美，更想去找寻城市里丢失已久的繁华喧嚣背后的那份宁静！\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/226-e1423481444208.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/226-e1423481444208.jpg\" alt=\"2\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-314\" /></a>\r\n一路上初冬的细雨绵绵不绝，淅淅沥沥，雨中的大明山，一切都在恍惚中扑面而来，恍惚了双眼恍惚了世间恍惚了彼此。各种不知名的树叶泛着的笔触无法形容的黄、红、橙，零星飘落摇曳枝头，却毫不吝啬厚厚的铺满整个山道。延绵山路萦绕曲伸，未几便无路可走，凌乱大小不一的石块错落横伸，泥泞中倒成为夯实的着脚点，手脚并用着在树根盘踞的野道上奋力向上向前。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/318-e1423481493990.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/318-e1423481493990.jpg\" alt=\"3\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-315\" /></a>\r\n越往上，雨不停雾更浓，梦里不知身是客！烟雨却晓户外情！群山罗列只在想象中，想要远眺，目光极处满是队伍中彼此狼狈不堪却亢奋不已的那股劲！\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/413.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/413.jpg\" alt=\"4\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-316\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/513-e1423481540900.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/513-e1423481540900.jpg\" alt=\"5\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-317\" /></a>\r\n扎营千亩草甸，不见一亩草只见雾迷茫。\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/613-e1423481568767.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/613-e1423481568767.jpg\" alt=\"6\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-318\" /></a>\r\n7岁半的丫丫当仁不让的被评选为队长！假以时日，必成大器！<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/713-e1423481600845.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/713-e1423481600845.jpg\" alt=\"7\" width=\"750\" height=\"1333\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-319\" /></a>\r\n作为领队，你这么负重有担当，我们一起竖起大拇哥！\r\n作为男生，你玉米胡萝卜香菇花生米一路扛着，你丈母娘知道要心疼死了！\r\n说好了，下次花生米小马哥背香菇我来背，也让我们偶尔重装一次，千万别客气！\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/87-e1423481622561.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/87-e1423481622561.jpg\" alt=\"8\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-320\" /></a>\r\n篝火旁，扑鼻的那个味道啊，随着浑身冉冉升起的仙气，汗酸味和脚臭味四处迷茫开来！\r\n赶紧的，排骨汤掀开，好歹冲淡一点这怪味！\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/97-e1423481649644.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/97-e1423481649644.jpg\" alt=\"9\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-321\" /></a>\r\n大明山顶，千亩草甸，仙境般的茫茫冬雨浓雾的晚上，冬雪松是没邂逅，夏雨荷也不知芳踪，有了这锅浓浓的货足料肥汤美的分享，小伙伴们欢声笑语穿破云雾挡住冬雨，生命在那瞬间火一样美丽绽放！<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/106-e1423481678602.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/106-e1423481678602.jpg\" alt=\"10\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-322\" /></a>\r\n此次冒雨穿越大明山，我们迎难而上，我们征服自己取悦自己！岁月很公平，因很多偶尔的决定变换着每个人成长轨迹，送给每个人的收获亦因了这份决定后的付出而呈现别样的精彩，我们的人生多了回忆多了念想多了珍惜！\r\n   只是因为多看了你一眼，从此我们开始行走思念！\r\n   感谢AA户外！感谢AK先生！感谢大明山的小伙伴们！\r\n   期待下一次！','大明湖畔夏雨荷，大明山上冬雨葱','','publish','open','open','','%e5%a4%a7%e6%98%8e%e6%b9%96%e7%95%94%e5%a4%8f%e9%9b%a8%e8%8d%b7%ef%bc%8c%e5%a4%a7%e6%98%8e%e5%b1%b1%e4%b8%8a%e5%86%ac%e9%9b%a8%e8%91%b1','','','2015-02-10 11:48:27','2015-02-10 03:48:27','',0,'http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/?p=312',0,'post','',0),(313,1,'2015-02-09 19:29:45','2015-02-09 11:29:45','','1','','inherit','open','open','','1-7','','','2015-02-09 19:29:45','2015-02-09 11:29:45','',312,'http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/120.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(314,1,'2015-02-09 19:29:45','2015-02-09 11:29:45','','2','','inherit','open','open','','2-9','','','2015-02-09 19:29:45','2015-02-09 11:29:45','',312,'http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/226.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(315,1,'2015-02-09 19:29:46','2015-02-09 11:29:46','','3','','inherit','open','open','','3-8','','','2015-02-09 19:29:46','2015-02-09 11:29:46','',312,'http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/318.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(316,1,'2015-02-09 19:29:47','2015-02-09 11:29:47','','4','','inherit','open','open','','4-8','','','2015-02-09 19:29:47','2015-02-09 11:29:47','',312,'http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/413.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(317,1,'2015-02-09 19:29:48','2015-02-09 11:29:48','','5','','inherit','open','open','','5-8','','','2015-02-09 19:29:48','2015-02-09 11:29:48','',312,'http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/513.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(318,1,'2015-02-09 19:29:48','2015-02-09 11:29:48','','6','','inherit','open','open','','6-8','','','2015-02-09 19:29:48','2015-02-09 11:29:48','',312,'http://www.mempie.com/cargroup/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/613.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(319,1,'2015-02-09 19:29:50','2015-02-09 11:29:50','','7','','inherit','open','open','','7-8','','','2015-02-09 19:29:50','2015-02-09 11:29: