>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">这一幕不禁叫人想到了张爱玲的《倾城之恋》，颇有一种管他周遭如何嘈杂纷扰，我们至少在这个空间时间里拥有了彼此的圆满感。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	（画外音：泥垢了！矫情你妹！无视我们这些单身狗吗？下一个！！！）\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/4-e1422845885835.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/4-e1422845885835.jpg\" alt=\"4\" width=\"750\" height=\"501\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-108\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><br />\r\n</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>最和谐互动奖</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">谁说和保安哥哥们就永远只有架吵？</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	也许以前是的。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	但洒下一把彩色粉就不一样鸟！\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	哈哈哈哈！\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/5-e1422845877689.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/5-e1422845877689.jpg\" alt=\"5\" width=\"750\" height=\"501\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-109\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>最拼跳高团组奖</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">感觉大家也都蛮拼的了，这个还是并列拿了吧！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/6-3-e1422845868664.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/6-3-e1422845868664.jpg\" alt=\"6-3\" width=\"750\" height=\"499\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-110\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>最萌熊孩子奖</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">一票小萝莉的乱入和表演相信萌化了所有人吧！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	熊孩子要萌成这样再怎么闹腾也只能打碎牙和血吞，忍了！\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/7-2-e1422845860620.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/7-2-e1422845860620.jpg\" alt=\"7-2\" width=\"750\" height=\"501\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-111\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><br />\r\n</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>最霸气抢镜王</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">这完全不需要解释了吧？</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	随便问谁全场最霸气最有镜头感最秒杀菲林的人物是谁，我相信回答都绝对都是她、她、她、她、她！！！\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	原谅小编实在是太喜欢这妞忍不住多放了几张照片：）\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/8-4-e1422845852838.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/8-4-e1422845852838.jpg\" alt=\"8-4\" width=\"750\" height=\"501\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-113\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><br />\r\n</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>最热心助人奖</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">细致耐心地帮阿（来，请跟我读：ǎ）姨把帐篷搭起来了有木有？看那认真专注的小眼神，超NICE！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	经门小派鉴定的好男银一枚，妞们快抢！\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/9-e1422845845278.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/9-e1422845845278.jpg\" alt=\"9\" width=\"750\" height=\"501\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-114\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<strong>最如沐春风广告植入奖</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">农夫山泉作为门派的特别合作伙伴为此次彩色跑活动提供了饮料支持，如此如沐春风春风化雨润物无声的广告植入估计大家都木有察觉到吧？！所以此奖理所应当颁给农夫山泉咯：）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	（你以为小编会告诉你通过门派购农夫山泉旗下产品有超低吐血折扣吗？某只傲娇地飘~飘~飘~过~）\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/10-e1422845836500.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/10-e1422845836500.jpg\" alt=\"10\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-115\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<strong>最职业吃货团</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">AA户外俱乐部又一次以充足的食材和器具准备、清晰明确有条不紊的组织分工协作和坚韧不拔走到哪吃到哪的吃货精神当之无愧赢得了本次最职业吃货团的称号！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"line