的慢城HAPPY&nbsp;DAY。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/31.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/31.jpg\" alt=\"3\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-629\" /></a><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/21-e1423478369102.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/21-e1423478369102.jpg\" alt=\"2\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-628\" /></a><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/51.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/51.jpg\" alt=\"5\" width=\"540\" height=\"595\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-631\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	浩浩荡荡的车队驶经机场高速、宁高高速，一路奔向高淳。车队抵达游人如织的高淳老街，全体车友代表赞助商“花样城”向路人们分发了代表美好祝福的黄玫瑰，现场的景象温情脉脉，十分醉人。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/41.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/41.jpg\" alt=\"4\" width=\"450\" height=\"800\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-630\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	当花语是“幸运”的黄色玫瑰从车队小伙伴的手中传递给路人，当金色的心形气球簇拥在一起，共同绽放。幸福的气息，就这样弥漫在高淳的蓝蓝天空下&nbsp;……\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/61-e1423478323451.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/61-e1423478323451.jpg\" alt=\"6\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-632\" /></a><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/71-e1423478304903.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/71-e1423478304903.jpg\" alt=\"7\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-633\" /></a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">高淳的秋天阳光正好，螃蟹正肥。赞助商为本次活动提供了丰盛的农家菜和螃蟹大餐，各大俱乐部的车友们欢聚一堂，共叙友谊，享受轻松愉快的假日时光。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/81.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/81.jpg\" alt=\"8\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-634\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">再次感谢各大车友会及其GM们：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	福特车友会\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	索纳塔车友会\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	新君威车友会\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	雅阁车友会\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">深情感谢本次HAPPY&nbsp;DAY的独家赞助商：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	花样年.花样城（由中国唯一上市物业公司提供服务）\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	南京高淳经济开发区/&nbsp;025-68507888\r\n</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />','车友俱乐部的慢城HAPPY DAY','','publish','open','open','','%e8%bd%a6%e5%8f%8b%e4%bf%b1%e4%b9%90%e9%83%a8%e7%9a%84%e6%85%a2%e5%9f%8ehappy-day','','','2015-02-09 21:06:55','2015-02-09 13:06:55','',0,'http://www.mempie.com/?p=181',0,'post','',0),(182,1,'2015-02-02 14:24:13','2015-02-02 06:24:13','','5','','inherit','open','open','','5-4','','','2015-02-02 14:24:13','2015-02-02 06:24:13','',181,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/53.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(183,1,'2015-02-02 14:24:18','2015-02-02 06:24:18','','6','','inherit','open','open','','6-2','','','2015-02-02 14:24:18','2015-02-02 06:24:18','',181,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/61.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(184,1,'2015-02-02 14:24:24','2015-02-02 06:24:24','','7','','inherit','open','open','','7-3','','','2015-02-02 14:24:24','2015-02-02 06:24:24','',181,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/71.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(185,1,'2015-02-02 14:24:30','2015-02-02 06:24:30','','8','','inherit','open','open','','8-2','','','2015-02-02 14:24:30','2015-02-02 06:24:30','',181,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/81.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(186,1,'2015-02-02 14:24:35','2015-02-02 06:24:35','','1','','inherit','open','open','','1','','','2015-02-02 14:24:35','2015-02-02 06: