le=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n		领队：俞斌老师\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n		社群：怪兽卡车越野工场\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n		&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;南京奔驰车友会·星驰会&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n		&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;仁恒翠竹园邻居会\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n		&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;南京义工联\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n		&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;大叔的舞蹈工作室和他的朋友们\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n		以及：匿名爱心人士\r\n	</p>\r\n</p>','单身妹纸+乌镇浪漫一夜','互联网大会召开之际，门派送出本月免费福利','inherit','open','open','','207-revision-v1','','','2015-02-02 15:24:48','2015-02-02 07:24:48','',207,'http://www.mempie.com/?p=208',0,'revision','',0),(209,1,'2015-02-02 15:48:06','2015-02-02 07:48:06','','052-IMG_8929','','inherit','open','open','','052-img_8929','','','2015-02-02 15:48:06','2015-02-02 07:48:06','',207,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/052-IMG_8929.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(210,1,'2015-02-02 15:48:19','2015-02-02 07:48:19','','086-IMG_7507','','inherit','open','open','','086-img_7507','','','2015-02-02 15:48:19','2015-02-02 07:48:19','',207,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/086-IMG_7507.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(211,1,'2015-02-02 15:48:32','2015-02-02 07:48:32','','090-IMG_7519','','inherit','open','open','','090-img_7519','','','2015-02-02 15:48:32','2015-02-02 07:48:32','',207,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/090-IMG_7519.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(212,1,'2015-02-02 15:48:45','2015-02-02 07:48:45','','IMG_6660(0)','','inherit','open','open','','img_66600','','','2015-02-02 15:48:45','2015-02-02 07:48:45','',207,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_66600.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(213,1,'2015-02-02 15:48:59','2015-02-02 07:48:59','','IMG_6663(0)','','inherit','open','open','','img_66630','','','2015-02-02 15:48:59','2015-02-02 07:48:59','',207,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_66630.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(214,1,'2015-02-02 15:49:09','2015-02-02 07:49:09','','IMG_6676(0)','','inherit','open','open','','img_66760','','','2015-02-02 15:49:09','2015-02-02 07:49:09','',207,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_66760.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(215,1,'2015-02-02 15:52:14','2015-02-02 07:52:14','<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	2014年平安夜，我们在一个偏僻山村的学校里度过了一个有趣的晚上。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	门派网络召集的64位志愿者分乘18辆车，自驾500多公里，带着圣诞节礼物，下午4：00如约来到安徽省金寨县天堂寨镇后畈村。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_66600.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_66600.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_6660(0)\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-212\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	这个村子位于大别山深处，典型的山区村落，村口是一所希望小学，有200多名学生，都是附近普通农民的孩子，大部分是留守儿童——父母进城打工，孩子们吃住都在这所学校。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	艰难的山路，美丽的风景\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/052-IMG_8929.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/052-IMG_8929.jpg\" alt=\"052-IMG_8929\" width=\"750\" height=\"501\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-209\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	乡村道路狭窄，学校里也没有停车位，长长的车队停在学校外的路口，60多名志愿者和前来接应的孩子们一起，把一箱一箱的礼物搬进了学校。黄校长说，虽然学校常有公益组织和爱心人士来捐助，但第一次有这么多人来和学生们共度节日，孩子们非常兴奋。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/086-IMG_7507.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/086-IMG_7507.jpg\" alt=\"086-IMG_7507\" width=\"750\" height=\"501\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-210\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	晚上六点多钟，我们搭起了一棵圣诞树，点燃了篝火，志愿者和小学生们轮番表演节目，来自艺术社团的舞蹈老师带领孩子们跳舞、游戏，简陋的音响、寒冷的天气丝毫没减弱大家的兴致，附近的村民们都抱着小孩子来凑热闹，后畈村小学小小的操场上簇拥了几百人，山村的冬夜，难得有这么热闹的景致。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_66630.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_66630.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_6663(0)\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-213\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	没有欢迎仪式，没有煽情表演，我们希望给山村小学留下一份陌生人的善意和有趣的回忆。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	参加本次“山村平安夜”门派联合行动的志愿者来自南京、苏州、常州、无锡、上海几个城市的车友会、义工组织、大学生社团和邻居会。门派邀请了有“中国好人”称号的著名公益人士——退休老教师俞斌担任领队。所有参加活动的成员共采购了15,000元的礼物，门派网络作为发起者，为志愿者们安排了一顿简单的山村晚宴。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/090-IMG_7519-e1422863381403.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/090-IMG_7519-e1422863381403.jpg\" alt=\"090-IMG_7519\" width=\"750\" height=\"501\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-211\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_66760.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_66760.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_6676(0)\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-214\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	本次行动，我们经与校方讨论，不安排欢迎仪式、不安排集体合影、不安排贫困儿童作陪、不安排助学捐款，我们只想——表达一份纯粹的善意。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	我们希望藉此行动，提倡一种有趣而简单的社群活动方式：把结伴旅游和公益行动结合起来。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	1、如果结伴去较为偏远的地方旅游，在旅游的途中，不妨花一点心思，顺路捎带些东西给有需要的人（&nbsp;例如学校、乡村、福利机构&nbsp;）；\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	2、提前联系，事先征求别人的同意；&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	3、尽可能准备别人确实需要的物品；&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	4、即送即走，以双方愉悦为原则。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	作为一个致力于社群联合运营的互联网平台，我们将乐于组织各大社群开展类似的活动，并为大家争取赞助商的支持。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	感谢:\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	领队：俞斌老师\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">社群：怪兽卡车越野工场</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;南京奔驰车友会·星驰会&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;仁恒翠竹园邻居会\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;南京义工联\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;大叔的舞蹈工作室和他的朋友们\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">以及：匿名爱心人士</span>\r\n</p>','大别山里的圣诞节','','inherit','open','open','','207-revision-v1','','','2015-02-02 15:52:14','2015-02-02 07:52:14','',207,'http://www.mempie.com/?p=215',0,'revision','',0),(216,1,'2015-01-01 00:00:10','2014-12-31 16:00:10','<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片4.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片4.jpg\" alt=\"图片4\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-695\" /></a>世界上，能在2014年12月31日最后一刻还在路上奔跑的人有几个&nbsp;？</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">多年以后，我们会告诉孩子们，这一夜是这样度过的……</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片15.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片15.jpg\" alt=\"图片15\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-702\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">在2014年的最后一夜，来自18个社群超过2000个朋友聚集在门派联合行动“五星电器Runners’&nbsp;night奔腾夜”的现场。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片21.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片21.jpg\" alt=\"图片21\" width=\"750\" height=\"419\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-705\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">这一夜有激光、音乐和劲舞，有延绵数百米漫山遍野的夜跑队伍，有汗水、笑声和响彻夜空的新年祝福。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">这一夜，闪亮的队伍跑过城市与山峦&nbsp;，一直跑向2015年的钟声敲响。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片18.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片18.jpg\" alt=\"图片18\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-704\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片5.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片5.jpg\" alt=\"图片5\" width=\"750\" height=\"492\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-696\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">这是一个独特而难忘的夜晚，这是一个闪耀的夜晚，这是一个告别过去的夜晚，这是一个迎接崭新生活的夜晚。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片17.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片17.jpg\" alt=\"图片17\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-703\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片12.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片12.jpg\" alt=\"图片12\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-700\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">在多年以后，我们回忆2014的时候，每个人都会记得，这一年的最后一刻，我们正跑在路上。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片10.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片10.jpg\" alt=\"图片10\" width=\"750\" height=\"489\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-698\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">酷炫性感的激光舞掀开了这次跑步者大会的帷幕。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片11.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片11.jpg\" alt=\"图片11\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-699\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">南师大的黑人舞者用一场双人斗舞为大家临行助威。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">当我们在路上，延亘数公里漫山遍野闪烁的光点，是我们奔跑的步伐，我们闪耀、我们奔跑，我们用这样最闪亮的方式，一路狂奔直达2015。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/dadadad.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/dadadad.jpg\" alt=\"dadadad\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-707\" /></a><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">We&nbsp;Are&nbsp;Runners,We&nbsp;Are&nbsp;Winners！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片2.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片2.jpg\" alt=\"图片2\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-693\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">当我们归来，我们赢得了2015年的第一枚奖章。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">在2014最后的时刻，我们一起倒数计时，在拥抱欢舞中迎来属于我们的崭新的2015！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">We&nbsp;Are&nbsp;Runners，We&nbsp;Are&nbsp;Stars！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片3.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片3.jpg\" alt=\"图片3\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-694\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">我们是今夜南京最潮的明星。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">来自伦敦的唱片骑师Neil将全场气氛拉至最高潮，当我们随着电音的节奏跳动摇摆，我们用最时尚的方式庆祝属于我们未来的驾到。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">2015，我们来了！RUNNERS，加油！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>','既然已经出发，我们必须奔跑','','publish','open','open','','%e6%97%a2%e7%84%b6%e5%b7%b2%e7%bb%8f%e5%87%ba%e5%8f%91%ef%bc%8c%e6%88%91%e4%bb%ac%e5%bf%85%e9%a1%bb%e5%a5%94%e8%b7%91','','','2015-02-10 16:37:02','2015-02-10 08:37:02','',0,'http://www.mempie.com/?p=216',0,'post','',0),(217,1,'2015-02-02 16:08:29','2015-02-02 08:08:29','','IMG_8195','','inherit','open','open','','img_8195','','','2015-02-02 16:08:29','2015-02-02 08:08:29','',216,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_8195.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(218,1,'2015-02-02 16:08:39','2015-02-02 08:08:39','','图片1','','inherit','open','open','','%e5%9b%be%e7%89%871','','','2015-02-02 16:08:39','2015-02-02 08:08:39','',216,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/图片1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(219,1,'2015-02-02 16:08:55','2015-02-02 08:08:55','','图片2','','inherit','open','open','','%e5%9b%be%e7%89%872','','','2015-02-02 16:08:55','2015-02-02 08:08:55','',216,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/图片2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(220,1,'2015-02-02 16:09:15','2015-02-02 08:09:15','','图片3','','inherit','open','open','','%e5%9b%be%e7%89%873','','','2015-02-02 16:09:15','2015-02-02 08:09:15','',216,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/图片3.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(221,1,'2015-02-02 16:09:22','2015-02-02 08:09:22','','图片4','','inherit','open','open','','%e5%9b%be%e7%89%874','','','2015-02-02 16:09:22','2015-02-02 08:09:22','',216,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/图片4.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(222,1,'2015-02-02 16:09:29',