ent/uploads/2015/02/图片17.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(230,1,'2015-02-02 16:10:26','2015-02-02 08:10:26','','图片18','','inherit','open','open','','%e5%9b%be%e7%89%8718','','','2015-02-02 16:10:26','2015-02-02 08:10:26','',216,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/图片18.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(231,1,'2015-02-02 16:10:32','2015-02-02 08:10:32','','图片21','','inherit','open','open','','%e5%9b%be%e7%89%8721','','','2015-02-02 16:10:32','2015-02-02 08:10:32','',216,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/图片21.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(232,1,'2015-02-02 16:11:04','2015-02-02 08:11:04','','主画面','','inherit','open','open','','%e4%b8%bb%e7%94%bb%e9%9d%a2','','','2015-02-02 16:11:04','2015-02-02 08:11:04','',216,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/主画面.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(233,1,'2015-02-02 16:11:08','2015-02-02 08:11:08','','dadadad','','inherit','open','open','','dadadad','','','2015-02-02 16:11:08','2015-02-02 08:11:08','',216,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/dadadad.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(234,1,'2015-02-02 16:12:03','2015-02-02 08:12:03','','主画面','','inherit','open','open','','%e4%b8%bb%e7%94%bb%e9%9d%a2-2','','','2015-02-02 16:12:03','2015-02-02 08:12:03','',216,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/主画面1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(235,1,'2015-02-02 16:18:10','2015-02-02 08:18:10','<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/%E4%B8%BB%E7%94%BB%E9%9D%A21.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/%E4%B8%BB%E7%94%BB%E9%9D%A21.jpg\" alt=\"主画面\" width=\"750\" height=\"395\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-234\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	这个世界上，能在2014年12月31日最后一刻还在路上奔跑的人有几个&nbsp;？\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">多年以后，我们会告诉孩子们，这一夜是这样度过的……</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8712.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8712.jpg\" alt=\"图片12\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-226\" /></a><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	在2014年的最后一夜，来自18个社群超过2000个朋友聚集在门派联合行动“五星电器Runners’&nbsp;night奔腾夜”的现场。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%871.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%871.jpg\" alt=\"图片1\" width=\"750\" height=\"451\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-218\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%875.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%875.jpg\" alt=\"图片5\" width=\"750\" height=\"492\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8721.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8721.jpg\" alt=\"图片21\" width=\"750\" height=\"419\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-231\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">这一夜有激光、音乐和劲舞，有延绵数百米漫山遍野的夜跑队伍，有汗水、笑声和响彻夜空的新年祝福。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">这一夜，闪亮的队伍跑过城市与山峦&nbsp;，一直跑向2015年的钟声敲响。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/dadadad.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/dadadad.jpg\" alt=\"dadadad\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233\" /></a><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">这是一个独特而难忘的夜晚，这是一个闪耀的夜晚，这是一个告别过去的夜晚，这是一个迎接崭新生活的夜晚。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8718.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8718.jpg\" alt=\"图片18\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230\" /></a><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8717.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8717.jpg\" alt=\"图片17\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229\" /></a><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">在多年以后，我们回忆2014的时候，每个人都会记得，这一年的最后一刻，我们正跑在路上。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8710.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8710.jpg\" alt=\"图片10\" width=\"750\" height=\"489\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224\" /></a>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	酷炫性感的激光舞掀开了这次跑步者大会的帷幕。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8711.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8711.jpg\" alt=\"图片11\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	南师大的黑人舞者用一场双人斗舞为大家临行助威。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	当我们在路上，延亘数公里漫山遍野闪烁的光点，是我们奔跑的步伐，我们闪耀、我们奔跑，我们用这样最闪亮的方式，一路狂奔直达2015。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	We&nbsp;Are&nbsp;Runners,We&nbsp;Are&nbsp;Winners！\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%872.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%872.jpg\" alt=\"图片2\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-219\" /></a>&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	当我们归来，我们赢得了2015年的第一枚奖章。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	在2014最后的时刻，我们一起倒数计时，在拥抱欢舞中迎来属于我们的崭新的2015！\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	We&nbsp;Are&nbsp;Runners，We&nbsp;Are&nbsp;Stars！\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%874.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%874.jpg\" alt=\"图片4\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-221\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	我们是今夜南京最潮的明星。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	来自伦敦的唱片骑师Neil将全场气氛拉至最高潮，当我们随着电音的节奏跳动摇摆，我们用最时尚的方式庆祝属于我们未来的驾到。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	2015，我们来了！RUNNERS，加油！\r\n</p>\r\n</span><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/图片3.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/图片3.jpg\" alt=\"图片3\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-220\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/图片9.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/图片9.jpg\" alt=\"图片9\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/图片13.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/图片13.jpg\" alt=\"图片13\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-227\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/图片15.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/图片15.jpg\" alt=\"图片15\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228\" /></a> &nbsp;&nbsp;','既然已经出发，我们必须奔跑','','inherit','open','open','','216-revision-v1','','','2015-02-02 16:18:10','2015-02-02 08:18:10','',216,'http://www.mempie.com/?p=235',0,'revision','',0),(236,1,'2015-02-02 16:21:15','2015-02-02 08:21:15','<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	2014年平安夜，我们在一个偏僻山村的学校里度过了一个有趣的晚上。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	门派网络召集的64位志愿者分乘18辆车，自驾500多公里，带着圣诞节礼物，下午4：00如约来到安徽省金寨县天堂寨镇后畈村。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_66600.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_66600.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_6660(0)\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-212\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	这个村子位于大别山深处，典型的山区村落，村口是一所希望小学，有200多名学生，都是附近普通农民的孩子，大部分是留守儿童——父母进城打工，孩子们吃住都在这所学校。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	艰难的山路，美丽的风景\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/052-IMG_8929.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/052-IMG_8929.jpg\" alt=\"052-IMG_8929\" width=\"750\" height=\"501\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-209\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	乡村道路狭窄，学校里也没有停车位，长长的车队停在学校外的路口，60多名志愿者和前来接应的孩子们一起，把一箱一箱的礼物搬进了学校。黄校长说，虽然学校常有公益组织和爱心人士来捐助，但第一次有这么多人来和学生们共度节日，孩子们非常兴奋。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/086-IMG_7507.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/086-IMG_7507.jpg\" alt=\"086-IMG_7507\" width=\"750\" height=\"501\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-210\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	晚上六点多钟，我们搭起了一棵圣诞树，点燃了篝火，志愿者和小学生们轮番表演节目，来自艺术社团的舞蹈老师带领孩子们跳舞、游戏，简陋的音响、寒冷的天气丝毫没减弱大家的兴致，附近的村民们都抱着小孩子来凑热闹，后畈村小学小小的操场上簇拥了几百人，山村的冬夜，难得有这么热闹的景致。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_66630.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_66630.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_6663(0)\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-213\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	没有欢迎仪式，没有煽情表演，我们希望给山村小学留下一份陌生人的善意和有趣的回忆。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	参加本次“山村平安夜”门派联合行动的志愿者来自南京、苏州、常州、无锡、上海几个城市的车友会、义工组织、大学生社团和邻居会。门派邀请了有“中国好人”称号的著名公益人士——退休老教师俞斌担任领队。所有参加活动的成员共采购了15,000元的礼物，门派网络作为发起者，为志愿者们安排了一顿简单的山村晚宴。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/090-IMG_7519-e1422863381403.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/090-IMG_7519-e1422863381403.jpg\" alt=\"090-IMG_7519\" width=\"750\" height=\"501\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-211\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_66760.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_66760.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_6676(0)\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-214\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	本次行动，我们经与校方讨论，不安排欢迎仪式、不安排集体合影、不安排贫困儿童作陪、不安排助学捐款，我们只想——表达一份纯粹的善意。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	我们希望藉此行动，提倡一种有趣而简单的社群活动方式：把结伴旅游和公益行动结合起来。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	1、如果结伴去较为偏远的地方旅游，在旅游的途中，不妨花一点心思，顺路捎带些东西给有需要的人（&nbsp;例如学校、乡村、福利机构&nbsp;）；\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	2、提前联系，事先征求别人的同意；&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	3、尽可能准备别人确实需要的物品；&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	4、即送即走，以双方愉悦为原则。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	作为一个致力于社群联合运营的互联网平台，我们将乐于组织各大社群开展类似的活动，并为大家争取赞助商的支持。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	感谢:\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	领队：俞斌老师\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">社群：怪兽卡车越野工场</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;南京奔驰车友会·星驰会&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;仁恒翠竹园邻居会\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;南京义工联\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;大叔的舞蹈工作室和他的朋友们\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">以及：匿名爱心人士</span> \r\n</p>','大别山里的圣诞节','','inherit','open','open','','207-revision-v1','','','2015-02-02 16:21:15','2015-02-02 08:21:15','',207,'http://www.mempie.com/?p=236',0,'revision','',0),(237,1,'2015-01-11 16:40:16','2015-01-11 08:40:16','<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20150209125643_33462.png\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:14px;\">从哈雷到马术，从电影到木作，从骑行到摇滚，不同的圈子，不同的喜好，但又同是一帮热爱生活追求品质的玩家聚到一起，到底碰撞出了怎样的火花？</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:14px;\">2015年1月11日,门派与骋望云邸联手举办的例外生活俱乐部正式启动，绽放出了一场花样百出别开生面的跨社群联欢盛会。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20150209125741_82407.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20150209125741_56720.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:14px;\">精彩有爱的跨界交流，自娱自乐的新鲜玩法。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20150209125839_82692.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20150209125839_97513.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:14px;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:14px;\">一次美奂绝伦的例外之秀，一场各类社群的联欢盛会。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20150209125932_15404.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:14px;\">有趣的人，有趣的事。这就是我们的例外生活俱乐部。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20150209130003_45029.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:14px;\">1月11日，当15个社群代表在LED大屏上同时摁下手印时，宣告了俱乐部于2015年1月25日举行的“悠游紫金山”大型登山活动正式启动。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:14px;\">这15个社群分别是：</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:14px;\">终极机车俱乐部&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:14px;\">国际赛马场马术俱乐部</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:14px;\">苏宁易购小丫快跑</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:14px;\">AA户外俱乐部</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:14px;\">南京悦跑俱乐部</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:14px;\">南京DS车友会</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:14px;\">骓驰车影俱乐部</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:14px;\">登南京紫金山俱乐部</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:14px;\">小迎星艺术团妈妈群</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:14px;\">沈博士学术交流群</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:14px;\">南京齐放放映</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:14px;\">我们爱摇滚音乐电影群</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:14px;\">罗辑思维会员群</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:14px;\">我们爱木作</span