ef=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/33.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/33.jpg\" alt=\"3\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-251\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/83.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/83.jpg\" alt=\"8\" width=\"750\" height=\"750\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-255\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/133.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/133.jpg\" alt=\"13\" width=\"750\" height=\"478\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-241\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/103.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/103.jpg\" alt=\"10\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-239\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20.jpg\" alt=\"20\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-247\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	1月11日，当15个社群代表在LED大屏上同时摁下手印时，宣告了俱乐部于2015年1月25日举行的“悠游紫金山”大型登山活动正式启动。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/73.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/73.jpg\" alt=\"7\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-254\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	这15个社群分别是：\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	终极机车俱乐部&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	国际赛马场马术俱乐部\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	苏宁易购小丫快跑\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	AA户外俱乐部\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	南京悦跑俱乐部\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	南京DS车友会\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	骓驰车影俱乐部\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	登南京紫金山俱乐部\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	小迎星艺术团妈妈群\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	沈博士学术交流群\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	南京齐放放映\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	我们爱摇滚音乐电影群\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	罗辑思维会员群\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	我们爱木作\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	南京体院教师群\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">本次“悠游紫金山”活动由骋望云邸全情赞助支持，并提供了价值总额2万元的登山奖金。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/43.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/43.jpg\" alt=\"4\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-252\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/55.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/55.jpg\" alt=\"5\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-253\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	我们爱玩，我们更懂得玩。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">2015，和门派，我们一起玩出新花样！</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	在这个满屏段子的碎片化互联网时代，网络社群的强大力量已经逐渐凸显，能玩会闹很重要，但想要和如上社群一样玩出真金白银的赞助来，还需要社群联盟的整合力量，更需要有趣有爱的玩法。大家需要的，正是门派这样的社群平台，带着社群一起占便宜谋福利。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">2015年，社群+门派+赞助商，我们一起玩出新花样！</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	社群加入请勾搭：王小姐&nbsp;139-1597-3325\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	赞助商请联系：毛先生&nbsp;139-1393-4907&nbsp;/&nbsp;章小姐&nbsp;180-1391-8380\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/55.jpg\"></a>\r\n</p>','平淡的生活需要新鲜的玩法','','inherit','open','open','','237-revision-v1','','','2015-02-02 16:40:16','2015-02-02 08:40:16','',237,'http://www.mempie.com/?p=256',0,'revision','',0),(257,1,'2015-01-20 16:56:13','2015-01-20 08:56:13','<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20150209123647_87776.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">俗人看武媚娘，无非是个“胸”字，雅人看武媚娘，却是那一段盛世追忆和绝代风华。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">在武媚娘的时代，香道、茶道、挂画和插花被称为“四雅”、“四般闲事”，成为上流社会的一种生活态度。传闻武则天在被召临幸之前沐浴、焚香缺一不可。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">史海沉浮，从唐朝宫廷内帷到现代都市生活，一簇香，一盏茶，有多少故事。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">腊月初五（1月24日）下午14时，门派首次雅集聚会，相约高科·荣境。以三款名茶、数十种沉香、木器、宝石、陶器款待南京城诸雅士。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20150209123817_45759.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><strong>致境·雅集</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">世间熙攘，大多人被时代洪流推着庸碌前行，茫茫然不知其终。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">与其随波逐流，被时代所裹挟，我更愿退后一步，回归自身。焚香品茶、把玉玩器，在器皿玩物间悠然自处，于熙攘闹市寻方寸宁静，闲暇间与三五好友相聚，坐而论其道。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">人生乐事，不过如此。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">01 论香</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">燃点一簇香，于满室幽香中，中国美院硕士研究生、国家一级香道师岳潇副教授为我们论说了用香之道的缘起兴衰，讲述沉香和一支烟如何奇妙混合。并与嘉宾一同通过眼观、手触、鼻嗅等品香形式，对各类名贵香料进行了全身心的鉴赏和感悟，闻香气、观香具、阔论香道。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20150209123947_46188.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20150209124012_58150.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">02 斗茶</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">有市无价的顶级熟普，私人珍藏的陈年生普，最热门的正山小种……</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">一器成名只为茗，悦来客满是茶香。最典雅的陈设布置，最精致的汝窑茶器，最顶级的诸类茶种，均为款待最雅致的茶客。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">上有侯琦老师为在场的茶客解说茶道，解惑答疑，侧有司炉烫壶温杯，分茶敬之，诸位茶客于茶香扑鼻中得解茶道之惑，于清冽甘甜间品茶艺之妙。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20150209124053_26363.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">03 玩器</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">玩物乃志，赏器皆雅，毕业于中国美术学院的雕塑家、收藏家侯琦先生为大家解说珠串盘捻把玩间的诸般奇妙。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">景德镇陶瓷世家传人、南京故宫博物院的陶艺师王创先生则以匠工精神带大家现场手制陶器，在盘捏揉作间为大家细细阐述了古法柴烧陶器的冰火淬炼之奥。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20150209124138_27340.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20150209124213_85025.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">04 射覆</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">古有李商隐诗云“隔座送钩春酒暖，分曹射覆蜡灯红”，“射覆”即是古代文人集会时常玩的猜物游戏之一，我们将在焚香品茶之余，&nbsp;今行古趣，以诗文为射，以字物为覆，胜者以茶器赠之，由此展开了一场饶有趣味的现代射覆之旅。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"></span><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20150209124249_56562.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">美好的情感需要物质来承载,繁忙的生活需要偶尔的留白.偶得闲情与三五知音好友相聚，焚香品茶、把玉玩器，实乃人间乐事。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">门派与高科荣境携手举办的首届雅集盛会在盎然雅趣间完美落幕，感谢所有前来捧场的社群诸友：</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">南京各大高校EMBA同学会</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">南京各大高校教师群</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">南京钟山高尔夫球会</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">南京国际赛马场俱乐部</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">南京宝马车友俱乐部</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">南京奔驰车友俱乐部</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">南京奥迪车友俱乐部</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">紫东国际创意园区企业高管</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">徐庄软件园区企业高管</span>\r\n</p>','君非俗人，请来一聚','','publish','open','open','','%e5%90%9b%e9%9d%9e%e4%bf%97%e4%ba%ba%ef%bc%8c%e8%af%b7%e6%9d%a5%e4%b8%80%e8%81%9a','','','2015-02-09 20:49:22','2015-02-09 12:49:22','',0,'http://www.mempie.com/?p=257',0,'post','',0),(258,1,'2015-02-02 16:45:41','2015-02-02 08:45:41','','IMG_9625','','inherit','open','open','','img_9625','','','2015-02-02 16:45:41','2015-02-02 08:45:41','',257,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9625.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(259,1,'2015-02-02 16:45:53','2015-02-02 08:45:53','','IMG_9684','','inherit','open','open','','img_9684','','','2015-02-02 16:45:53','2015-02-02 08:45:53','',257,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9684.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(260,1,'2015-02-02 16:46:02','2015-02-02 08:46:02','','IMG_9700','','inherit','open','open','','img_9700','','','2015-02-02 16:46:02','2015-02-02 08:46:02','',257,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9700.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(261,1,'2015-02-02 16:46:16','2015-02-02 08:46:16','','IMG_9719','','inherit','open','open','','img_9719','','','2015-02-02 16:46:16','2015-02-02 08:46:16','',257,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9719.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(262,1,'2015-02-02 16:46:26','2015-02-02 08:46:26','','IMG_9723','','inherit','open','open','','img_9723','','','2015-02-02 16:46:26','2015-02-02 08:46:26','',257,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9723.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(263,1,'2015-02-02 16:46:38','2015-02-02 08:46:38','','IMG_9816','','inherit','open','open','','img_9816','','','2015-02-02 16:46:38','2015-02-02 08:46:38','',257,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9816.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(264,1,'2015-02-02 16:46:50','2015-02-02 08:46:50','','IMG_9862','','inherit','open','open','','img_9862','','','2015-02-02 16:46:50','2015-02-02 08:46:50','',257,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9862.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(265,1,'2015-02-02 16:47:02','2015-02-02 08:47:02','','IMG_9892','','inherit','open','open','','img_9892','','','2015-02-02 16:47:02','2015-02-02 08:47:02','',257,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9892.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(266,1,'2015-02-02 16:47:16','2015-02-02 08:47:16','','IMG_9928','','inherit','open','open','','img_9928','','','2015-02-02 16:47:16','2015-02-02 08:47:16','',257,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9928.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(267,1,'2015-02-02 16:47:27','2015-02-02 08:47:27','','IMG_9952','','inherit','open','open','','img_9952','','','2015-02-02 16:47:27','2015-02-02 08:47:27','',257,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9952.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(268,1,'2015-02-02 16:47:40','2015-02-02 08:47:40','','IMG_0024','','inherit','open','open','','img_0024','','','2015-02-02 16:47:40','2015-02-02 08:47:40','',257,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_0024.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(269,1,'2015-02-02 16:48:02','2015-02-02 08:48:02','','IMG_0046','','inherit','open','open','','img_0046','','','2015-02-02 16:48:02','2015-02-02 08:48:02','',257,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_0046.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(270,1,'2015-02-02 16:53:41','2015-02-02 08:53:41','','IMG_9995','','inherit','open','open','','img_9995','','','2015-02-02 16:53:41','2015-02-02 08:53:41','',257,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9995.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(271,1,'2015-02-02 16:56:13','2015-02-02 08:56:13','<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	俗人看武媚娘，无非是个“胸”字，雅人看武媚娘，却是那一段盛世追忆和绝代风华。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	在武媚娘的时代，香道、茶道、挂画和插花被称为“四雅”、“四般闲事”，成为上流社会的一种生活态度。传闻武则天在被召临幸之前沐浴、焚香缺一不可。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	史海沉浮，从唐朝宫廷内帷到现代都市生活，一簇香，一盏茶，有多少故事。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9625.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9625.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_9625\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-258\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	腊月初五（1月24日）下午14时，门派首次雅集聚会，相约高科·荣境。以三款名茶、数十种沉香、木器、宝石、陶器款待南京城诸雅士。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9684.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9684.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_9684\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-259\" /></a>&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">致境·雅集</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	美好的情感需要物质来承载\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	世间熙攘，大多人被时代洪流推着庸碌前行，茫茫然不知其终。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	与其随波逐流，被时代所裹挟，我更愿退后一步，回归自身。焚香品茶、把玉玩器，在器皿玩物间悠然自处，于熙攘闹市寻方寸宁静，闲暇间与三五好友相聚，坐而论其道。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	人生乐事，不过如此。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9719.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9719.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_9719\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-261\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	论香\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	燃点一簇香，于满室幽香中，中国美院硕士研究生、国家一级香道师岳潇副教授为我们论说了用香之道的缘起兴衰，讲述沉香和一支烟如何奇妙混合。并与嘉宾一同通过眼观、手触、鼻嗅等品香形式，对各类名贵香料进行了全身心的鉴赏和感悟，闻香气、观香具、阔论香道。<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9862.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9862.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_9862\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-264\" /></a><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9928.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9928.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_9928\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-266\" /></a><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	斗茶\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	有市无价的顶级熟普，私人珍藏的陈年生普，最热门的正山小种……\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	一器成名只为茗，悦来客满是茶香。最典雅的陈设布置，最精致的汝窑茶器，最顶级的诸类茶种，均为款待最雅致的茶客。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	上有侯琦老师为在场的茶客解说茶道，解惑答疑，侧有司炉烫壶温杯，分茶敬之，诸位茶客于茶香扑鼻中得解茶道之惑，于清冽甘甜间品茶艺之妙。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9723.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9723.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_9723\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-262\" /></a><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"> </span><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9816.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9816.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_9816\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-263\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	玩器\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	玩物乃志，赏器皆雅，毕业于中国美术学院的雕塑家、收藏家侯琦先生为大家解说珠串盘捻把玩间的诸般奇妙。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	景德镇陶瓷世家传人、南京故宫博物院的陶艺师王创先生则以匠工精神带大家现场手制陶器，在盘捏揉作间为大家细细阐述了古法柴烧陶器的冰火淬炼之奥。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_0024.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_0024\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-268\" /><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_0046.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_0046.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_0046\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-269\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	射覆\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	古有李商隐诗云“隔座送钩春酒暖，分曹射覆蜡灯红”，“射覆”即是古代文人集会时常玩的猜物游戏之一，我们将在焚香品茶之余，&nbsp;今行古趣，以诗文为射，以字物为覆，胜者以茶器赠之，由此展开了一场饶有趣味的现代射覆之旅。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9995.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9995.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_9995\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-270\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<p class=\"p15\">\r\n		美好的情感需要物质来承载<span>,</span><span>繁忙的生活需要偶尔的留白</span><span>.</span><span>偶得闲情与三五知音好友相聚，焚香品茶、把玉玩器，实乃人间乐事。</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"p15\">\r\n		门派与高科荣境携手举办的首届雅集盛会在盎然雅趣间完美落幕，感谢所有前来捧场的社群诸友：\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"p15\">\r\n		南京各大高校<span>EMBA</span><span>同学会</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"p15\">\r\n		南京各大高校教师群\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"p15\">\r\n		南京钟山高尔夫球会\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"p15\">\r\n		南京国际赛马场俱乐部\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"p15\">\r\n		南京宝马车友俱乐部\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"p15\">\r\n		南京奔驰车友俱乐部\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"p15\">\r\n		南京奥迪车友俱乐部\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"p15\">\r\n		紫东国际创意园区企业高管\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"p15\">\r\n		徐庄软件园区企业高管\r\n	</p>\r\n</p>','君非俗人，请来一聚','','inherit','open','open','','257-revision-v1','','','2015-02-02 16:56:13','2015-02-02 08:56:13','',257,'http://www.mempie.com/?p=271',0,'revision','',0),(272,1,'2015-02-02 16:57:41','2015-02-02 08:57:41','<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	俗人看武媚娘，无非是个“胸”字，雅人看武媚娘，却是那一段盛世追忆和绝代风华。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	在武媚娘的时代，香道、茶道、挂画和插花被称为“四雅”、“四般闲事”，成为上流社会的一种生活态度。传闻武则天在被召临幸之前沐浴、焚香缺一不可。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	史海沉浮，从唐朝宫廷内帷到现代都市生活，一簇香，一盏茶，有多少故事。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9625.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9625.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_9625\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-258\" /