派和骋望云邸联手举办的“致趣紫金山——千人High翻紫金山”大型登山赛事。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/3-e1423469687890.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/3-e1423469687890.jpg\" alt=\"图片3\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-304\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span></span><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/4-e1423470238168.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/4-e1423470238168.jpg\" alt=\"图片4\" width=\"750\" height=\"497\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-305\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span></span><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/5-e1423470314836.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/5-e1423470314836.jpg\" alt=\"图片5\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-306\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">有皇上亲率后宫诸人穿越而来</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/图片6.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/6-e1423470328469.jpg\" alt=\"图片6\" width=\"750\" height=\"421\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-307\" /></a><span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/7-e1423470342673.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/7-e1423470342673.jpg\" alt=\"图片7\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-308\" /></a><span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/8-e1423469652261.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/8-e1423469652261.jpg\" alt=\"图片8\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-309\" /></a></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	有马术协会身骑骏马驰骋开道\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/9-e1423470360609.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/9-e1423470360609.jpg\" alt=\"图片9\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-310\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/10-e1423470372680.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/10-e1423470372680.jpg\" alt=\"图片10\" width=\"750\" height=\"693\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-311\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/11-e1423470385973.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/11-e1423470385973.jpg\" alt=\"图片11\" width=\"750\" height=\"469\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-312\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	有武媚娘外星人VS狗狗团的奇异篇章\r\n</p>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/12-e1423470398902.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/12-e1423470398902.jpg\" alt=\"图片12\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-313\" /></a>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/图片13.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/13-e1423470416156.jpg\" alt=\"图片13\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-314\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/14-e1423470426225.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/14-e1423470426225.jpg\" alt=\"图片14\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-315\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	有哈雷车队载着姑娘轰鸣助阵\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/16-e1423470472319.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/16-e1423470472319.jpg\" alt=\"图片16\" width=\"750\" height=\"557\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-317\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/15-e1423470439318.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/15-e1423470439318.jpg\" alt=\"图片15\" width=\"750\" height=\"557\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-316\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	有聋哑单车车队一路骑行跋涉\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/17-e1423470498643.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/17-e1423470498643.jpg\" alt=\"图片17\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-318\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/18-e1423470509187.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/18-e1423470509187.jpg\" alt=\"图片18\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-319\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	也有竞速选手为着速度奋力冲刺\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/图片19.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/图片19.jpg\" alt=\"图片19\" width=\"720\" height=\"960\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-320\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">从年仅14岁的稚嫩少年到78岁的不老斗士。从骨折未愈拄拐花7小时也要坚强完赛的61岁马拉哥，到一路欢乐无声乐行公益的聋哑骑士……</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20-e1423470522892.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20-e1423470522892.jpg\" alt=\"图片20\" width=\"750\" height=\"557\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-321\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	大家盛装而来，扛着队旗翻山越岭，一路荣耀前行。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	经过20KM翻山越岭的艰难旅程，最终共有957人抵达了终点，各自收获了一枚令人难忘的完赛奖章。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	本来，在各自的小圈子里安分守己互不干涉，才是这个世界的生存法则。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	可总有那么一些人，他们用非凡的创造力和凝聚力为大家一次次创造生活的美好。他们用跨界交流的耀眼火花为大家展示了生活的另一种有趣可能。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/5E79B885-BC00-4E83-B4C1-F008B37F2163-e1423472000580.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/5E79B885-BC00-4E83-B4C1-F008B37F2163-e1423472000580.jpg\" alt=\"5E79B885-BC00-4E83-B4C1-F008B37F2163\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-432\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	这是门派的第17次联合行动，这半年来，我们有过争执，有过困惑，但始终一个信念未曾动摇：就是为各类社群提供一个可以互相交流的平台，做有爱、有趣、有力量的各种事。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	而这力量，正是来源于你们，这一群群热爱生活的小伙伴们。因为你们，我们相信，我们的路还有很长，我们的活动会绽放出越来越璀璨的光芒！\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	下一站，我们的三人篮球争霸赛将在3月份热血登场，请诸位继续热烈关注和参与！\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	既然我们生来不凡，何必甘于平庸？！\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	那，就绽放吧！\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	——————————————————\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">附：</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong>“致趣紫金山”竞速组获奖名单</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	第一名，奖金3000元：\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	中山铁人三项俱乐部 程乾育\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	第二名，奖金1000元：\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	紫金山登山群 王煜\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	第三名，奖金500元：\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	马鞍山市铁人三项运动协会 赵军\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong>“致趣紫金山”创意造型奖获奖社群</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	南京天生爱跑步\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong>“致趣紫金山”生活风尚奖获奖社群</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	南京聪行骑友会\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>','我们正在开创大场面！','','publish','open','open','','%e6%88%91%e4%bb%ac%e6%ad%a3%e5%9c%a8%e5%bc%80%e5%88%9b%e5%a4%a7%e5%9c%ba%e9%9d%a2%ef%bc%81','','','2015-02-09 17:05:58','2015-02-09 09:05:58','',0,'http://www.mempie.com/?p=297',0,'post','',0),(298,1,'2015-02-06 22:20:30','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','自动草稿','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2015-02-06 22:20:30','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://www.mempie.com/?p=298',0,'post','',0),(299,1,'2015-02-06 22:21:55','2015-02-06 14:21:55','<p>\r\n	俗人看武媚娘，无非是个“胸”字，雅人看武媚娘，却是那一段盛世追忆和绝代风华。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	在武媚娘的时代，香道、茶道、挂画和插花被称为“四雅”、“四般闲事”，成为上流社会的一种生活态度。传闻武则天在被召临幸之前沐浴、焚香缺一不可。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	史海沉浮，从唐朝宫廷内帷到现代都市生活，一簇香，一盏茶，有多少故事。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9625.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9625.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_9625\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-258\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	腊月初五（1月24日）下午14时，门派首次雅集聚会，相约高科·荣境。以三款名茶、数十种沉香、木器、宝石、陶器款待南京城诸雅士。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9684.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9684.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_9684\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-259\" /></a>&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">致境·雅集</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">美好的情感需要物质来承载</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	世间熙攘，大多人被时代洪流推着庸碌前行，茫茫然不知其终。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	与其随波逐流，被时代所裹挟，我更愿退后一步，回归自身。焚香品茶、把玉玩器，在器皿玩物间悠然自处，于熙攘闹市寻方寸宁静，闲暇间与三五好友相聚，坐而论其道。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	人生乐事，不过如此。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9719.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9719.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_9719\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-261\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">论香</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	燃点一簇香，于满室幽香中，中国美院硕士研究生、国家一级香道师岳潇副教授为我们论说了用香之道的缘起兴衰，讲述沉香和一支烟如何奇妙混合。并与嘉宾一同通过眼观、手触、鼻嗅等品香形式，对各类名贵香料进行了全身心的鉴赏和感悟，闻香气、观香具、阔论香道。<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9862.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9862.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_9862\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-264\" /></a><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9928.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9928.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_9928\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-266\" /></a><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	斗茶\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	有市无价的顶级熟普，私人珍藏的陈年生普，最热门的正山小种……\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	一器成名只为茗，悦来客满是茶香。最典雅的陈设布置，最精致的汝窑茶器，最顶级的诸类茶种，均为款待最雅致的茶客。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	上有侯琦老师为在场的茶客解说茶道，解惑答疑，侧有司炉烫壶温杯，分茶敬之，诸位茶客于茶香扑鼻中得解茶道之惑，于清冽甘甜间品茶艺之妙。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9723.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9723.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_9723\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-262\" /></a><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"> </span><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9816.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9816.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_9816\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-263\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	玩器\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	玩物乃志，赏器皆雅，毕业于中国美术学院的雕塑家、收藏家侯琦先生为大家解说珠串盘捻把玩间的诸般奇妙。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	景德镇陶瓷世家传人、南京故宫博物院的陶艺师王创先生则以匠工精神带大家现场手制陶器，在盘捏揉作间为大家细细阐述了古法柴烧陶器的冰火淬炼之奥。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_0024.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_0024\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-268\" /><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_0046.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_0046.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_0046\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-269\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">射覆</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	古有李商隐诗云“隔座送钩春酒暖，分曹射覆蜡灯红”，“射覆”即是古代文人集会时常玩的猜物游戏之一，我们将在焚香品茶之余，&nbsp;今行古趣，以诗文为射，以字物为覆，胜者以茶器赠之，由此展开了一场饶有趣味的现代射覆之旅。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9995.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/IMG_9995.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_9995\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-270\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">美好的情感需要物质来承载</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">,</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">繁忙的生活需要偶尔的留白</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">.</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">偶得闲情与三五知音好友相聚，焚香品茶、把玉玩器，实乃人间乐事。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	门派与高科荣境携手举办的首届雅集盛会在盎然雅趣间完美落幕，感谢所有前来捧场的社群诸友：\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	南京各大高校<span>EMBA</span><span>同学会</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	南京各大高校教师群\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	南京钟山高尔夫球会\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	南京国际赛马场俱乐部\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	南京宝马车友俱乐部\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	南京奔驰车友俱乐部\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	南京奥迪车友俱乐部\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	紫东国际创意园区企业高管\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	徐庄软件园区企业高管\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>','君非俗人，请来一聚','','inherit','open','open','','257-revision-v1','','','2015-02-06 22:21:55','2015-02-06 14:21:55','',257,'http://www.mempie.com/?p=299',0,'revision','',0),(300,1,'2015-02-08 11:12:05','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','自动草稿','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2015-02-08 11:12:05','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://www.mempie.com/?p=300',0,'post','',0),(301,1,'2015-02-08 11:18:45','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','自动草稿','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2015-02-08 11:18:45','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://www.mempie.com/?page_id=301',0,'page','',0),(302,1,'2015-02-09 15:59:36','2015-02-09 07:59:36','','图片1','','inherit','open','open','','%e5%9b%be%e7%89%871-2','','','2015-02-09 15:59:36','2015-02-09 07:59:36','',297,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/图片1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(303,1,'2015-02-09 15:59:39','2015-02-09 07:59:39','','图片2','','inherit','open','open','','%e5%9b%be%e7%89%872-2','','','2015-02-09 15:59:39','2015-02-09 07:59:39','',297,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/图片2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(304,1,'2015-02-09 15:59:42','2015-02-09 07:59:42','','图片3','','inherit','open','open','','%e5%9