','open','','10-9','','','2015-02-09 19:42:02','2015-02-09 11:42:02','',191,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/10.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(679,1,'2015-02-09 19:42:04','2015-02-09 11:42:04','','11','','inherit','open','open','','11-9','','','2015-02-09 19:42:04','2015-02-09 11:42:04','',191,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/11.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(680,1,'2015-02-09 19:42:06','2015-02-09 11:42:06','','12','','inherit','open','open','','12-8','','','2015-02-09 19:42:06','2015-02-09 11:42:06','',191,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/12.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(681,1,'2015-02-09 19:42:06','2015-02-09 11:42:06','','13','','inherit','open','open','','13-9','','','2015-02-09 19:42:06','2015-02-09 11:42:06','',191,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/13.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(682,1,'2015-02-09 19:48:28','2015-02-09 11:48:28','<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/1.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/1.jpg\" alt=\"1\" width=\"750\" height=\"453\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-669\" /></a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">2014年11月11日，森林摩尔商业街区，夜色中，伴着漫天飘洒的飞雪，我们的11.11“致青春”舞会深情拉开帷幕。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/2.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/2.jpg\" alt=\"2\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-670\" /></a><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/3.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/3.jpg\" alt=\"3\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-671\" /></a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">来自14所南京高校和20多个社群的嘉宾在闪光灯的包围下由红毯步入舞池，过足了一把奥斯卡的瘾。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/4.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/4.jpg\" alt=\"4\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-672\" /></a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">随着致青春的曼妙旋律，随着双人维也纳华尔兹华丽深情的舞步，我们的双十一“致青春”舞会唯美开场。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/5.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/5.jpg\" alt=\"5\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-673\" /></a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">这是一次主题舞会派对，也是一场不同年龄、不同时代的情侣们对青春和爱情的集体追忆。迎着飘雪机制造的南京2014年的第一场雪，大家纷纷牵起身边人的手，在舞者旋转步伐的引导下步入舞池。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/6.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/6.jpg\" alt=\"6\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-674\" /></a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">一曲热情怀旧的玫瑰玫瑰我爱你勾起了所有人身体里韵动的热情，大家与舞者们交织起舞。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/7.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/7.jpg\" alt=\"7\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-675\" /></a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">动情感人的嘉宾分享。南瓜夫妻是大学同学，相识相恋于1996年南航校园，那时正是老狼的民谣风靡校园的时刻，他们就在恋恋风尘的歌声中相恋，并一同携手走过了18个春秋。昨天晚上，他们一家三口依偎在一起又听到了这首歌。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/8.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/8.jpg\" alt=\"8\" width=\"750\" height=\"597\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-676\" /></a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">索允浩，一名17岁的打工少年，他没有和在场嘉宾一样有无忧无虑的校园时光，而是14岁起就背井离乡在外闯荡，他用他不一样的青春故事感动了在场所有人。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/9.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/9.jpg\" alt=\"9\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-677\" /></a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">欢舞一刻，来自娜美Salsa舞蹈培训学校的Nana老师用她热烈而曼妙的舞姿让全场跟着韵律开始舞动。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/11.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/11.jpg\" alt=\"11\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-679\" /></a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">指定搭讪的互动游戏让全场的小伙伴们尖叫连连。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/11.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/11.jpg\" alt=\"11\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-679\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	Party&nbsp;Queen和Party&nbsp;King的评选环节。女神男神齐上阵，贴满全身的爱心，洋溢着幸福的微笑，感染了所有人。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/12.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/12.jpg\" alt=\"12\" width=\"750\" height=\"600\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-680\" /></a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">最后，在深情相拥的悠扬歌声中，天空中再次飘起了雪，大家在造雪机营造的浪漫雪夜星空下，在这最后一首曲子中相拥而舞，纪念共同度过的这么一个浪漫而深情的夜晚。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/13.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/13.jpg\" alt=\"13\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-681\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	我们是一些平凡的人，大家通过互联网互相联系，共同策划和组织了一场舞会，听了一些好听的歌，跳了一场动人的舞曲。这个晚上，如同大家的青春，也许平凡，但独一无二。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	再次深情感谢以下社群伙伴们的协作支持\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	南京奔驰车友俱乐部·星驰会\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	在宁高校拉丁舞集训班\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	南京娜美Salsa舞蹈培训学校\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	大叔的舞蹈工作室\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	南京财经大学国标舞协会\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	东南大学成贤学院EGO拉丁舞社\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	南京理工大学交谊舞社团\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	南京农业大学国标舞社团\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	南京理工大学拉丁舞社团\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	南京林业大学交谊舞协会\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	南京审计学院交谊舞协会\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	河海大学拉丁舞协会\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	晓庄魅之舞拉丁社\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	也再次感谢我们给力的赞助商小伙伴们\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	南京森林摩尔商业街区\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	南京联通“选4G就选沃”\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	Aux奥克斯空调“好变频1度到天明”\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<br />','11.11致青春舞会，一起来看2014南京冬天的第一场雪','','inherit','open','open','','191-revision-v1','','','2015-02-09 19:48:28','2015-02-09 11:48:28','',191,'http://www.mempie.com/?p=682',0,'revision','',0),(683,1,'2015-02-09 19:53:09','2015-02-09 11:53:09','','未标题-2','','inherit','open','open','','%e6%9c%aa%e6%a0%87%e9%a2%98-2-3','','','2015-02-09 19:53:09','2015-02-09 11:53:09','',87,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/未标题-2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(684,1,'2015-02-09 19:56:50','2015-02-09 11:56:50','','未标题-2','','inherit','open','open','','%e6%9c%aa%e6%a0%87%e9%a2%98-2-4','','','2015-02-09 19:56:50','2015-02-09 11:56:50','',0,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/未标题-2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(685,1,'2015-02-09 20:06:22','2015-02-09 12:06:22','','052-IMG_8929','','inherit','open','open','','052-img_8929-2','','','2015-02-09 20:06:22','2015-02-09 12:06:22','',207,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/052-IMG_8929.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(686,1,'2015-02-09 20:06:24','2015-02-09 12:06:24','','086-IMG_7507','','inherit','open','open','','086-img_7507-2','','','2015-02-09 20:06:24','2015-02-09 12:06:24','',207,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/086-IMG_7507.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(687,1,'2015-02-09 20:06:26','2015-02-09 12:06:26','','090-IMG_7519','','inherit','open','open','','090-img_7519-2','','','2015-02-09 20:06:26','2015-02-09 12:06:26','',207,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/090-IMG_7519.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(688,1,'2015-02-09 20:06:27','2015-02-09 12:06:27','','IMG_6660(0)','','inherit','open','open','','img_66600-2','','','2015-02-09 20:06:27','2015-02-09 12:06:27','',207,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/IMG_66600.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(689,1,'2015-02-09 20:06:30','2015-02-09 12:06:30','','IMG_6663(0)','','inherit','open','open','','img_66630-2','','','2015-02-09 20:06:30','2015-02-09 12:06:30','',207,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/IMG_66630.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(690,1,'2015-02-09 20:06:32','2015-02-09 12:06:32','','IMG_6676(0)','','inherit','open','open','','img_66760-2','','','2015-02-09 20:06:32','2015-02-09 12:06:32','',207,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/IMG_66760.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(691,1,'2015-02-09 20:12:03','2015-02-09 12:12:03','<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">2014年平安夜，我们在一个偏僻山村的学校里度过了一个有趣的晚上。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/IMG_66600.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/IMG_66600.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_6660(0)\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-688\" /></a></span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">门派网络召集的64位志愿者分乘18辆车，自驾500多公里，带着圣诞节礼物，下午4：00如约来到安徽省金寨县天堂寨镇后畈村。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/IMG_66630.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/IMG_66630.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_6663(0)\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-689\" /></a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">这个村子位于大别山深处，典型的山区村落，村口是一所希望小学，有200多名学生，都是附近普通农民的孩子，大部分是留守儿童——父母进城打工，孩子们吃住都在这所学校。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	艰难的山路，美丽的风景\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/090-IMG_7519.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/090-IMG_7519.jpg\" alt=\"090-IMG_7519\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-687\" /></a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">乡村道路狭窄，学校里也没有停车位，长长的车队停在学校外的路口，60多名志愿者和前来接应的孩子们一起，把一箱一箱的礼物搬进了学校。黄校长说，虽然学校常有公益组织和爱心人士来捐助，但第一次有这么多人来和学生们共度节日，孩子们非常兴奋。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/IMG_66760.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/IMG_66760.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_6676(0)\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-690\" /></a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">晚上六点多钟，我们搭起了一棵圣诞树，点燃了篝火，志愿者和小学生们轮番表演节目，来自艺术社团的舞蹈老师带领孩子们跳舞、游戏，简陋的音响、寒冷的天气丝毫没减弱大家的兴致，附近的村民们都抱着小孩子来凑热闹，后畈村小学小小的操场上簇拥了几百人，山村的冬夜，难得有这么热闹的景致。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/086-IMG_7507.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/086-IMG_7507.jpg\" alt=\"086-IMG_7507\" width=\"750\" height=\"501\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-686\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	没有欢迎仪式，没有煽情表演，我们希望给山村小学留下一份陌生人的善意和有趣的回忆。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	参加本次“山村平安夜”门派联合行动的志愿者来自南京、苏州、常州、无锡、上海几个城市的车友会、义工组织、大学生社团和邻居会。门派邀请了有“中国好人”称号的著名公益人士——退休老教师俞斌担任领队。所有参加活动的成员共采购了15,000元的礼物，门派网络作为发起者，为志愿者们安排了一顿简单的山村晚宴。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/052-IMG_8929.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/052-IMG_8929.jpg\" alt=\"052-IMG_8929\" width=\"750\" height=\"501\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-685\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	本次行动，我们经与校方讨论，不安排欢迎仪式、不安排集体合影、不安排贫困儿童作陪、不安排助学捐款，我们只想——表达一份纯粹的善意。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	我们希望藉此行动，提倡一种有趣而简单的社群活动方式：把结伴旅游和公益行动结合起来。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	1、如果结伴去较为偏远的地方旅游，在旅游的途中，不妨花一点心思，顺路捎带些东西给有需要的人（&nbsp;例如学校、乡村、福利机构&nbsp;）；\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	2、提前联系，事先征求别人的同意；&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	3、尽可能准备别人确实需要的物品；&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	4、即送即走，以双方愉悦为原则。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	作为一个致力于社群联合运营的互联网平台，我们将乐于组织各大社群开展类似的活动，并为大家争取赞助商的支持。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	感谢:\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	领队：俞斌老师\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">社群：怪兽卡车越野工场</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;南京奔驰车友会·星驰会&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;仁恒翠竹园邻居会\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;南京义工联\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;大叔的舞蹈工作室和他的朋友们\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">以及：匿名爱心人士</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<br />','大别山里的圣诞节','','inherit','open','open','','207-revision-v1','','','2015-02-09 20:12:03','2015-02-09 12:12:03','',207,'http://www.mempie.com/?p=691',0,'revision','',0),(692,1,'2015-02-09 20:16:36','2015-02-09 12:16:36','','图片1','','inherit','open','open','','%e5%9b%be%e7%89%871-4','','','2015-02-09 20:16:36','2015-02-09 12:16:36','',216,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/0