-09 20:16:57','2015-02-09 12:16:57','','IMG_8195','','inherit','open','open','','img_8195-2','','','2015-02-09 20:16:57','2015-02-09 12:16:57','',216,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/IMG_8195.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(709,1,'2015-02-09 20:27:48','2015-02-09 12:27:48','<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/IMG_8195.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/IMG_8195.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_8195\" width=\"1100\" height=\"580\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-708\" /></a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">这个世界上，能在2014年12月31日最后一刻还在路上奔跑的人有几个&nbsp;？</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">多年以后，我们会告诉孩子们，这一夜是这样度过的……</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片15.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片15.jpg\" alt=\"图片15\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-702\" /></a></span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">在2014年的最后一夜，来自18个社群超过2000个朋友聚集在门派联合行动“五星电器Runners’&nbsp;night奔腾夜”的现场。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片21.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片21.jpg\" alt=\"图片21\" width=\"750\" height=\"419\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-705\" /></a><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片4.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片4.jpg\" alt=\"图片4\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-695\" /></a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">这一夜有激光、音乐和劲舞，有延绵数百米漫山遍野的夜跑队伍，有汗水、笑声和响彻夜空的新年祝福。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">这一夜，闪亮的队伍跑过城市与山峦&nbsp;，一直跑向2015年的钟声敲响。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片18.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片18.jpg\" alt=\"图片18\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-704\" /></a><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片5.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片5.jpg\" alt=\"图片5\" width=\"750\" height=\"492\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-696\" /></a></span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">这是一个独特而难忘的夜晚，这是一个闪耀的夜晚，这是一个告别过去的夜晚，这是一个迎接崭新生活的夜晚。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片17.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片17.jpg\" alt=\"图片17\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-703\" /></a><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片12.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片12.jpg\" alt=\"图片12\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-700\" /></a></span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">在多年以后，我们回忆2014的时候，每个人都会记得，这一年的最后一刻，我们正跑在路上。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片10.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片10.jpg\" alt=\"图片10\" width=\"750\" height=\"489\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-698\" /></a></span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">酷炫性感的激光舞掀开了这次跑步者大会的帷幕。</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片11.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片11.jpg\" alt=\"图片11\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-699\" /></a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">南师大的黑人舞者用一场双人斗舞为大家临行助威。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	当我们在路上，延亘数公里漫山遍野闪烁的光点，是我们奔跑的步伐，我们闪耀、我们奔跑，我们用这样最闪亮的方式，一路狂奔直达2015。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/dadadad.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/dadadad.jpg\" alt=\"dadadad\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-707\" /></a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">We&nbsp;Are&nbsp;Runners,We&nbsp;Are&nbsp;Winners！</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片2.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片2.jpg\" alt=\"图片2\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-693\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	当我们归来，我们赢得了2015年的第一枚奖章。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	在2014最后的时刻，我们一起倒数计时，在拥抱欢舞中迎来属于我们的崭新的2015！\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	We&nbsp;Are&nbsp;Runners，We&nbsp;Are&nbsp;Stars！\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片3.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/图片3.jpg\" alt=\"图片3\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-694\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	我们是今夜南京最潮的明星。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	来自伦敦的唱片骑师Neil将全场气氛拉至最高潮，当我们随着电音的节奏跳动摇摆，我们用最时尚的方式庆祝属于我们未来的驾到。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	2015，我们来了！RUNNERS，加油！\r\n</p>\r\n</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;','既然已经出发，我们必须奔跑','','inherit','open','open','','216-revision-v1','','','2015-02-09 20:27:48','2015-02-09 12:27:48','',216,'http://www.mempie.com/?p=709',0,'revision','',0),(710,1,'2015-02-09 20:31:40','2015-02-09 12:31:40','','1','','inherit','open','open','','1-13','','','2015-02-09 20:31:40','2015-02-09 12:31:40','',257,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(711,1,'2015-02-09 20:31:40','2015-02-09 12:31:40','','2','','inherit','open','open','','2-14','','','2015-02-09 20:31:40','2015-02-09 12:31:40','',257,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(712,1,'2015-02-09 20:31:41','2015-02-09 12:31:41','','3','','inherit','open','open','','3-14','','','2015-02-09 20:31:41','2015-02-09 12:31:41','',257,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/3.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(713,1,'2015-02-09 20:31:41','2015-02-09 12:31:41','','4','','inherit','open','open','','4-12','','','2015-02-09 20:31:41','2015-02-09 12:31:41','',257,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/4.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(714,1,'2015-02-09 20:31:42','2015-02-09 12:31:42','','5','','inherit','open','open','','5-14','','','2015-02-09 20:31:42','2015-02-09 12:31:42','',257,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/5.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(715,1,'2015-02-09 20:31:43','2015-02-09 12:31:43','','6','','inherit','open','open','','6-10','','','2015-02-09 20:31:43','2015-02-09 12:31:43','',257,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/6.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(716,1,'2015-02-09 20:31:43','2015-02-09 12:31:43','','7','','inherit','open','open','','7-11','','','2015-02-09 20:31:43','2015-02-09 12:31:43','',257,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/7.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(717,1,'2015-02-09 20:31:44','2015-02-09 12:31:44','','8','','inherit','open','open','','8-11','','','2015-02-09 20:31:44','2015-02-09 12:31:44','',257,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/8.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(718,1,'2015-02-09 20:49:06','2015-02-09 12:49:06','<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20150209123647_87776.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">俗人看武媚娘，无非是个“胸”字，雅人看武媚娘，却是那一段盛世追忆和绝代风华。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">在武媚娘的时代，香道、茶道、挂画和插花被称为“四雅”、“四般闲事”，成为上流社会的一种生活态度。传闻武则天在被召临幸之前沐浴、焚香缺一不可。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">史海沉浮，从唐朝宫廷内帷到现代都市生活，一簇香，一盏茶，有多少故事。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">腊月初五（1月24日）下午14时，门派首次雅集聚会，相约高科·荣境。以三款名茶、数十种沉香、木器、宝石、陶器款待南京城诸雅士。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20150209123817_45759.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><strong>致境·雅集</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">世间熙攘，大多人被时代洪流推着庸碌前行，茫茫然不知其终。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">与其随波逐流，被时代所裹挟，我更愿退后一步，回归自身。焚香品茶、把玉玩器，在器皿玩物间悠然自处，于熙攘闹市寻方寸宁静，闲暇间与三五好友相聚，坐而论其道。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">人生乐事，不过如此。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">01 论香</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">燃点一簇香，于满室幽香中，中国美院硕士研究生、国家一级香道师岳潇副教授为我们论说了用香之道的缘起兴衰，讲述沉香和一支烟如何奇妙混合。并与嘉宾一同通过眼观、手触、鼻嗅等品香形式，对各类名贵香料进行了全身心的鉴赏和感悟，闻香气、观香具、阔论香道。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20150209123947_46188.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20150209124012_58150.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">02 斗茶</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">有市无价的顶级熟普，私人珍藏的陈年生普，最热门的正山小种……</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">一器成名只为茗，悦来客满是茶香。最典雅的陈设布置，最精致的汝窑茶器，最顶级的诸类茶种，均为款待最雅致的茶客。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">上有侯琦老师为在场的茶客解说茶道，解惑答疑，侧有司炉烫壶温杯，分茶敬之，诸位茶客于茶香扑鼻中得解茶道之惑，于清冽甘甜间品茶艺之妙。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20150209124053_26363.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">03 玩器</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">玩物乃志，赏器皆雅，毕业于中国美术学院的雕塑家、收藏家侯琦先生为大家解说珠串盘捻把玩间的诸般奇妙。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">景德镇陶瓷世家传人、南京故宫博物院的陶艺师王创先生则以匠工精神带大家现场手制陶器，在盘捏揉作间为大家细细阐述了古法柴烧陶器的冰火淬炼之奥。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20150209124138_27340.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20150209124213_85025.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">04 射覆</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">古有李商隐诗云“隔座送钩春酒暖，分曹射覆蜡灯红”，“射覆”即是古代文人集会时常玩的猜物游戏之一，我们将在焚香品茶之余，&nbsp;今行古趣，以诗文为射，以字物为覆，胜者以茶器赠之，由此展开了一场饶有趣味的现代射覆之旅。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"></span><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20150209124249_56562.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">美好的情感需要物质来承载,繁忙的生活需要偶尔的留白.偶得闲情与三五知音好友相聚，焚香品茶、把玉玩器，实乃人间乐事。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">门派与高科荣境携手举办的首届雅集盛会在盎然雅趣间完美落幕，感谢所有前来捧场的社群诸友：</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">南京各大高校EMBA同学会</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">南京各大高校教师群</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">南京钟山高尔夫球会</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">南京国际赛马场俱乐部</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">南京宝马车友俱乐部</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">南京奔驰车友俱乐部</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">南京奥迪车友俱乐部</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">紫东国际创意园区企业高管</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">徐庄软件园区企业高管</span>\r\n</p>','君非俗人，请来一聚','','inherit','open','open','','257-autosave-v1','','','2015-02-09 20:49:06','2015-02-09 12:49:06','',257,'http://www.mempie.com/?p=718',0,'revision','',0),(719,1,'2015-02-09 20:43:53','2015-02-09 12:43:53','<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20150209123647_87776.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	俗人看武媚娘，无非是个“胸”字，雅人看武媚娘，却是那一段盛世追忆和绝代风华。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	在武媚娘的时代，香道、茶道、挂画和插花被称为“四雅”、“四般闲事”，成为上流社会的一种生活态度。传闻武则天在被召临幸之前沐浴、焚香缺一不可。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	史海沉浮，从唐朝宫廷内帷到现代都市生活，一簇香，一盏茶，有多少故事。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	腊月初五（1月24日）下午14时，门派首次雅集聚会，相约高科·荣境。以三款名茶、数十种沉香、木器、宝石、陶器款待南京城诸雅士。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20150209123817_45759.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"><strong>致境·雅集</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"><strong>美好的情感需要物质来承载</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	世间熙攘，大多人被时代洪流推着庸碌前行，茫茫然不知其终。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	与其随波逐流，被时代所裹挟，我更愿退后一步，回归自身。焚香品茶、把玉玩器，在器皿玩物间悠然自处，于熙攘闹市寻方寸宁静，闲暇间与三五好友相聚，坐而论其道。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	人生乐事，不过如此。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"><strong>01 论香</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	燃点一簇香，于满室幽香中，中国美院硕士研究生、国家一级香道师岳潇副教授为我们论说了用香之道的缘起兴衰，讲述沉香和一支烟如何奇妙混合。并与嘉宾一同通过眼观、手触、鼻嗅等品香形式，对各类名贵香料进行了全身心的鉴赏和感悟，闻香气、观香具、阔论香道。<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20150209123947_46188.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20150209124012_58150.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<strong>02 斗茶</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	有市无价的顶级熟普，私人珍藏的陈年生普，最热门的正山小种……\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	一器成名只为茗，悦来客满是茶香。最典雅的陈设布置，最精致的汝窑茶器，最顶级的诸类茶种，均为款待最雅致的茶客。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	上有侯琦老师为在场的茶客解说茶道，解惑答疑，侧有司炉烫壶温杯，分茶敬之，诸位茶客于茶香扑鼻中得解茶道之惑，于清冽甘甜间品茶艺之妙。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20150209124053_26363.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<strong>03 玩器</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	玩物乃志，赏器皆雅，毕业于中国美术学院的雕塑家、收藏家侯琦先生为大家解说珠串盘捻把玩间的诸般奇妙。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	景德镇陶瓷世家传人、南京故宫博物院的陶艺师王创先生则以匠工精神带大家现场手制陶器，在盘捏揉作间为大家细细阐述了古法柴烧陶器的冰火淬炼之奥。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20150209124138_27340.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20150209124213_85025.jpg\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"><strong>04 射覆</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	古有李商隐诗云“隔座送钩春酒暖，分曹射覆蜡灯红”，“射覆”即是古代文人集会时常玩的猜物游戏之一，我们将在焚香品茶之余，&nbsp;今行古趣，以诗文为射，以字物为覆，胜者以茶器赠之，由此展开了一场饶有趣味的现代射覆之旅。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20150209124249_56562.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">美好的情感需要物质来承载</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">,</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">繁忙的生活需要偶尔的留白</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">.</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\">偶得闲情与三五知音好友相聚，焚香品茶、把玉玩器，实乃人间乐事。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	门派与高科荣境携手举办的首届雅集盛会在盎然雅趣间完美落幕，感谢所有前来捧场的社群诸友：\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	南京各大高校<span>EMBA</span><span>同学会</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	南京各大高校教师群\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	南京钟山高尔夫球会\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	南京国际赛马场俱乐部\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	南京宝马车友俱乐部\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	南京奔驰车友俱乐部\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	南京奥迪车友俱乐部\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	紫东国际创意园区企业高管\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	徐庄软件园区企业高管\r\n</p>','君非俗人，请来一聚','','inherit','open','open','','257-revision-v1','','','2015-02-09 20:43:53','2015-02-09 12:43:53','',257,'http://www.mempie.com/?p=719',0,'revision','',0),(720,1,'2015-02-09 20:45:50','2015-02-09 12:45:50','<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/20150209123647_87776.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	俗人看武媚娘，无非是个“胸”字，雅人看武媚娘，却是那一段盛世追忆和绝代风华。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	在武媚娘的时代，香道、茶道、挂画和插花被称为“四雅”、“四般闲事”，成为上流社会的一种生活态度。传闻武则天在被召临幸之前沐浴、焚香缺一不可。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	史海沉浮，从唐朝宫廷内帷到现代都市生活，一簇香，一盏茶，有多少故事。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	腊月初五（1月24日）下午14时，门派首次雅集聚会，相约高科·荣境。以三款名茶、数十种沉香、木器、宝石、陶器款待南京城诸雅士。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\