02','2015-02-10 08:37:02','',216,'http://www.mempie.com/?p=739',0,'revision','',0),(740,1,'2015-02-10 16:38:14','2015-02-10 08:38:14','<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	0月31日（周五），万圣节前夜，灵钟敲响的时候……\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	鬼王诏令万鬼齐聚Halloween&nbsp;Town\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/112.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/112.jpg\" alt=\"11\" width=\"650\" height=\"432\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-658\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">新街口，被清朝僵尸和吸血鬼围攻 &nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	大行宫，遇见血腥护士和恐怖狼人 &nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/122.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/122.jpg\" alt=\"12\" width=\"500\" height=\"752\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-659\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/141.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/141.jpg\" alt=\"14\" width=\"650\" height=\"432\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-660\" /></a><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">西安门，一大波僵尸上了地铁</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	孝陵卫，又出现一群电锯狂魔\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/IMG_8822.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/IMG_8822.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_8822\" width=\"650\" height=\"433\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-666\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/29.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/29.jpg\" alt=\"29\" width=\"650\" height=\"381\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-662\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	上千个鬼怪长途奔袭，\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	是一番暗无天日腥风血雨的末日之战&nbsp;？\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	还是一场对人类发起的联盟恐怖突击？\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">NO、NO、NO……</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	这是一场属于鬼魅妖魔的万鬼狂欢派对的开启仪式。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">由门派（一款集体主义的APP）免费提供全套化妆服饰</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	更有零食饮料、万圣节礼物等全程支援\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	这是南京史上规模最大的化妆大趴\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	120人的鬼怪游行队伍从新街口搭乘到仙林中心站，在金鹰奥莱城参加派对，我们的行动横跨半个城市，超过800位明星和嘉宾化妆参加演出，参加派对的观众累计达到21000多人！\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/IMG_8201.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/IMG_8201.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_8201\" width=\"650\" height=\"433\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-664\" /></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">最精致最正点的万圣节装扮</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p16\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">由大学生、教师等志愿者组成的化妆团队，在3个小时内，为超过800人化妆和造型（全部经费由赞助商筹集、所有参与者都获得一份值得纪念的万圣节装备）!</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p16\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/IMG_8816.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/IMG_8816.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_8816\" width=\"650\" height=\"433\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-665\" /></a></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	南京最大的一次集体舞\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p16\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">20：00，在雨中，在兔子舞的节奏中，台上台下的演员和观众共有上千人搭成火车，沿着金鹰奥莱城绕场巡游，携手共同完成了一场创记录的鬼怪集体巡游!</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">一次互联网用户的狂欢</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p16\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">一场真正的联欢派对，所有的表演嘉宾、主持人、化妆师、志愿者们全部通过网络招募和征选，全部由志愿者组成，来自30多个社群共同组织和筹划了这场规模盛大、没有年龄限制，幼青中老都尽享欢乐的超级万人派对！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">谢谢所有参与的社群团体：南京师范大学、南京邮电大学、南京财经大学、南理工、南信工、南林大、中科院植物研究所、奔驰车友会、DS车友会、猎人户外俱乐部、极速跑酷俱乐部、博世西门子、AA户外俱乐部、莲花新城邻居会、紫东国际创业园、徐庄软件园……</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">谢谢所有的赞助商们：南京联通、南京金鹰奥莱城、奥克斯空调、法国DS汽车……</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">谢谢所有的志愿者们！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">谢谢门派的小伙伴们！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">我们每一个单独的个体，</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	也许都微不足道。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	可当我们凝聚在一起，\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	我们就是最牛逼的！\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">请期待我们的下一站！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<br />','一场超过2万人参加的超级派对是怎样诞生的？','','inherit','open','open','','166-revision-v1','','','2015-02-10 16:38:14','2015-02-10 08:38:14','',166,'http://www.mempie.com/?p=740',0,'revision','',0),(741,1,'2015-02-10 16:39:53','2015-02-10 08:39:53','','1-IMGP1235','','inherit','open','open','','1-imgp1235-4','','','2015-02-10 16:39:53','2015-02-10 08:39:53','',143,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/1-IMGP12351.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(742,1,'2015-02-10 16:39:54','2015-02-10 08:39:54','','1','','inherit','open','open','','1-14','','','2015-02-10 16:39:54','2015-02-10 08:39:54','',143,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/16.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(743,1,'2015-02-10 16:39:54','2015-02-10 08:39:54','','2-IMG_8166','','inherit','open','open','','2-img_8166-4','','','2015-02-10 16:39:54','2015-02-10 08:39:54','',143,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2-IMG_81661.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(744,1,'2015-02-10 16:39:56','2015-02-10 08:39:56','','2-IMG_8357','','inherit','open','open','','2-img_8357-3','','','2015-02-10 16:39:56','2015-02-10 08:39:56','',143,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2-IMG_83571.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(745,1,'2015-02-10 16:39:57','2015-02-10 08:39:57','','2','','inherit','open','open','','2-15','','','2015-02-10 16:39:57','2015-02-10 08:39:57','',143,'http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/23.jpg',0,'attachment','imag