\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-558\" /></a><br />\r\n</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">假头套、洒水枪、墨镜、口罩等各种道具齐上阵……连T恤都尼玛撕烂了，最佳造型奖不给AA户外实在是天理不容人神共愤！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>最温暖亲情奖</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/23-e1423475128731.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/23-e1423475128731.jpg\" alt=\"2\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-559\" /></a></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">上阵父子兵，这位来自DS5车友会的爸爸带着儿子一起彩色跑堪称活动当中最温暖的一道风景线啦，这个爸爸看儿子的温暖眼神把路人小编都给融化啦！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>最老当益壮奖</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/33-e1423475097794.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/33-e1423475097794.jpg\" alt=\"3\" width=\"750\" height=\"501\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-560\" /></a></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">老大爷是1号选手，大概是本次活动参与者当中最为年长的了。但让人更为钦佩的是在第一名冲过终点大部队都开始转移阵地去烧烤去玩闹之后，老大爷仍然一个人坚持跑完了全程，大概持续到活动结束后二十分钟。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	满满32个赞！！！\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>最柔情蜜意奖</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/41-e1423475089986.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/41-e1423475089986.jpg\" alt=\"4\" width=\"750\" height=\"501\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-561\" /></a></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">这一幕不禁叫人想到了张爱玲的《倾城之恋》，颇有一种管他周遭如何嘈杂纷扰，我们至少在这个空间时间里拥有了彼此的圆满感。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	（画外音：泥垢了！矫情你妹！无视我们这些单身狗吗？下一个！！！）\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>最和谐互动奖</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/51-e1423475078820.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/51-e1423475078820.jpg\" alt=\"5\" width=\"750\" height=\"501\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-562\" /></a></strong><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">谁说和保安哥哥们就永远只有架吵？</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	也许以前是的。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	但洒下一把彩色粉就不一样鸟！\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	哈哈哈哈！\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>最拼跳高团组奖</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/6-11-e1423475060199.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/6-11-e1423475060199.jpg\" alt=\"6-1\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-563\" /></a></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/6-21-e1423475070173.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/6-21-e1423475070173.jpg\" alt=\"6-2\" width=\"750\" height=\"499\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-564\" /></a></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/6-3.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/6-3.jpg\" alt=\"6-3\" width=\"800\" height=\"532\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-763\" /></a>感觉大家也都蛮拼的了，这个还是并列拿了吧！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>最萌熊孩子奖</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/7-11-e1423475039370.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/7-11-e1423475039370.jpg\" alt=\"7-1\" width=\"750\" height=\"501\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-566\" /></a></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/7-21-e1423475002434.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/7-21-e1423475002434.jpg\" alt=\"7-2\" width=\"750\" height=\"501\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-567\" /></a></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/7-31-e1423475016992.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/7-31-e1423475016992.jpg\" alt=\"7-3\" width=\"750\" height=\"501\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-568\" /></a></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">一票小萝莉的乱入和表演相信萌化了所有人吧！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	熊孩子要萌成这样再怎么闹腾也只能打碎牙和血吞，忍了！\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>最霸气抢镜王</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/8-11-e1423474989950.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/8-11-e1423474989950.jpg\" alt=\"8-1\" width=\"750\" height=\"499\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-569\" /></a></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/8-21-e1423474979129.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/8-21-e1423474979129.jpg\" alt=\"8-2\" width=\"750\" height=\"501\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-570\" /></a></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/8-41-e1423474912782.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/8-41-e1423474912782.jpg\" alt=\"8-4\" width=\"750\" height=\"501\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-572\" /></a></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">这完全不需要解释了吧？</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	随便问谁全场最霸气最有镜头感最秒杀菲林的人物是谁，我相信回答都绝对都是她、她、她、她、她！！！\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	原谅小编实在是太喜欢这妞忍不住多放了几张照片：）\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><br />\r\n</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>最热心助人奖</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/91-e1423474895306.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/91-e1423474895306.jpg\" alt=\"9\" width=\"750\" height=\"501\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-573\" /></a></strong><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">细致耐心地帮阿（来，请跟我读：ǎ）姨把帐篷搭起来了有木有？看那认真专注的小眼神，超NICE！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	经门小派鉴定的好男银一枚，妞们快抢！\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<strong>最如沐春风广告植入奖</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<strong><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/101-e1423474887741.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/101-e1423474887741.jpg\" alt=\"10\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-574\" /></a></strong><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">农夫山泉作为门派的特别合作伙伴为此次彩色跑活动提供了饮料支持，如此如沐春风春风化雨润物无声的广告植入估计大家都木有察觉到吧？！所以此奖理所应当颁给农夫山泉咯：）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\">\r\n	（你以为小编会告诉你通过门派购农夫山泉旗下产品有超低吐血折扣吗？某只傲娇地飘~飘~飘~过~）\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<strong>最职业吃货团</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<strong><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/112-e1423474870799.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/112-e1423474870799.jpg\" alt=\"11\" width=\"750\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-575\" /></a></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<strong><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/12-31-e1423474860364.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/12-31-e1423474860364.jpg\" alt=\"12-3\" width=\"750\" height=\"499\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-578\" /></a></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<strong><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/12-41-e1423474836129.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/12-41-e1423474836129.jpg\" alt=\"12-4\" width=\"750\" height=\"501\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-579\" /></a></strong><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">AA户外俱乐部又一次以充足的食材和器具准备、清晰明确有条不紊的组织分工协作和坚韧不拔走到哪吃到哪的吃货精神当之无愧赢得了本次最职业吃货团的称号！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/131-e1423474844371.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/131-e1423474844371.jpg\" alt=\"13\" width=\"750\" height=\"501\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-580\" /></a></span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">必须给吃货团团长AK童鞋一个特写</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<strong>最神秘打酱油党</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<strong><a href=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/141-e1423474827967.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.mempie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/141-e1423474827967.jpg\" alt=\"14\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-581\" /></a></strong><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">某些个驱车几十里到句容然后窝到酒店打了一下午掼蛋吃了一顿饭完了还赶脚灰常充实滴筒子们，请对号入座！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">彩色跑高清无码大图集锦请戳新浪微盘：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Part1：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	http://vdisk.weibo.com/s/cofCO4DOc5Rw4\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Part2:</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	http://vdisk.weibo.com/s/cofCO4DOc5RwQ\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Part3：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	http://vdisk.weibo.com/s/cofCO4DOc5RwS&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Part4：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	http://vdisk.weibo.com/s/cofCO4DOc5Rwl&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Part5：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	http://vdisk.weibo.com/s/cofCO4DOc5RPF&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Part6：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p15\">\r\n	http://vdisk.weibo.com/s/cofCO4DOc5RPH\r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />','爱玩你就来，撒欢无止境！','','inherit','open','open','','97-revision-v1',